Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了\N{\rEng}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧 你是饿坏了吧\N{\rEng}There. You were hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子\N{\rEng}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:06.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读《农事诗》第三卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:13.37,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《农事诗》: 维吉尔(古罗马诗人)农业诗篇 论耕作与农事纷争】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）...终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）终有一日名扬四海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,继续念\N{\rEng}Repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Good day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,姑娘好\N{\rEng}Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你来休兰农场来做什么？\N{\rEng}What brings you to Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里教孩子\N{\rEng}I'm tutoring the boys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,教拉丁的先生啊\N{\rEng}The Latin tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过你\N{\rEng}I've heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你来这园里干什么？\N{\rEng}What brought you into the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...\N{\rEng}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就随便问问 教书先生\N{\rEng}It's just a question, master tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我 那个...\N{\rEng}Yes, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是出来透透气 而且...\N{\rEng}I suppose the air was fresh out here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我看到你带着只鸟\N{\rEng}uh, I saw you with your bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是只鹰 - 哦\N{\rEng}- It's a hawk. - Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能上前看看吗？\N{\rEng}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别凑太近\N{\rEng}Don't get too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他没见过你\N{\rEng}He doesn't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 小家伙\N{\rEng}Hello, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 哈哈哈\N{\rEng}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜欢你\N{\rEng}He likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？\N{\rEng}What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别打听\N{\rEng}I shan't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就打听\N{\rEng}You shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不说\N{\rEng}I shan't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你会说的 - 我不会\N{\rEng}- You shall. - I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等我亲你时你就会说了\N{\rEng}You'll tell me when we kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫安妮丝\N{\rEng}My name is Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你家哪儿的？\N{\rEng}Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我说错话了吗？\N{\rEng}Have I said something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊？ - 没有\N{\rEng}- Huh? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不知道我是谁 - 等下 我能去你...\N{\rEng}- You don't know who I am. - Wait, I wish to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你别再来找我了\N{\rEng}You can't see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了？\N{\rEng}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我下地帮巴塞洛缪\N{\rEng}I was in the field helping Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小羊崽病了\N{\rEng}A newborn lamb is unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我也去地里了\N{\rEng}Well, I... I went to the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可没见你啊\N{\rEng}I did not see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实在那儿 巴塞洛缪哥 你给她说说\N{\rEng}Well, I was there. Tell her, Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她确实在那里\N{\rEng}She was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过新来的拉丁先生吗？\N{\rEng}Have you seen the new Latin tutor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是皮匠的儿子\N{\rEng}The glover's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们说他上着上着课跑掉了 就再没回来\N{\rEng}The boys said he just ran out, never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他是来教书还债的\N{\rEng}He was supposed to give them lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还他父亲的债\N{\rEng}to pay off his father's debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我没见过他\N{\rEng}I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 早该料到\N{\rEng}Well, should've known better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,父子都一个德行\N{\rEng}Like father, like son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩可是咱们这教区最美的姑娘\N{\rEng}You know, I do believe you are the prettiest girls in the parish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 将来...\N{\rEng}- We are. - One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,会有许多人上门提亲\N{\rEng}I shall have my wits about me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲自把关 准把你们嫁个好人家\N{\rEng}for all the suitors that will come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝是大姐 还轮不到我们\N{\rEng}Agnes is the eldest. She'll marry first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她成天往树林里跑 像个流浪女\N{\rEng}She will not if she keeps running off to the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会娶她？\N{\rEng}like a gypsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们说... - 你去哪儿了?\N{\rEng}- When they said... - Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都等你好几个钟头了\N{\rEng}We were expecting you hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在... - 说啊\N{\rEng}- I was... - Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我在忙事儿\N{\rEng}I was working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\rEng}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快坐下吧\N{\rEng}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,饭菜都凉了\N{\rEng}Your supper's near cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别闹 别闹 - 别抢\N{\rEng}- Uh, boys, boys! - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 住手 - 大家都有份 别抢\N{\rEng}- Stop. - There's enough for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,休兰农场那边教得怎么样？\N{\rEng}How go the lessons at Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那些孩子不是读书的料\N{\rEng}Those boys are no scholars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就纳闷 他们读书有啥用 - 嗯\N{\rEng}- I wonder at the notion of all that learning. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,注定务农的孩子学拉丁文？\N{\rEng}Latin for boys who will be naught but sheep farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 用来装模做样吗？ - 不 不 不\N{\rEng}- It is the putting on of airs. - No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 够了 - 都给你 吉尔伯特\N{\rEng}- That will do! - All right, Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,听你娘的 都有份 别争\N{\rEng}You heard your mother. There's enough for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你说休兰那帮孩子不好\N{\rEng}You speak ill of the boys at Hewlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“不是读书的料”\N{\rEng}"They're no scholars."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可我跟你说 他们将来...\N{\rEng}But I tell you something,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,比你更像个男子汉\N{\rEng}they'll ever be more of a man than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人家将来有正经活 你没有\N{\rEng}They are put to honest work, unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你没出息 没手艺 只会装模做样\N{\rEng}Useless, tradeless, your fancy airs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,读那么多书\N{\rEng}All that education,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一点用都没有\N{\rEng}not an ounce of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我这没出息的去教书\N{\rEng}I'm tutoring those boys to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是替你还那户人家的债吗？\N{\rEng}your debts to that family, am I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠休兰家那么多债\N{\rEng}Your immeasurable amount of debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是我... 住手\N{\rEng}Didn't I help you... Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,休兰那边其他人\N{\rEng}What of the rest of the family at Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你都见过吗？\N{\rEng}Have you met them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只见过那户的母亲\N{\rEng}The mother only.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那大女儿没见到吗？ - 没有\N{\rEng}- Not the eldest daughter? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都说 那姑娘是森林巫婆的后代 \N{\rEng}It is said the girl is the child of a forest witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我就见过 她独自走在山路上\N{\rEng}I've seen her, wandering the back roads alone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,臂上还有只鹰\N{\rEng}with a hawk on her arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,休兰那儿还有鹰？\N{\rEng}A hawk at Hewlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,传言说她每次进林都是一个人带着那只鹰\N{\rEng}They say she takes him to the forest with her unaccompanied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗 伊莱莎？\N{\rEng}Yeah, but are you certain, Eliza?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那拿着鹰的是长女 不是仆人？\N{\rEng}The eldest daughter keeps a hawk, not a servant girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是仆人 我确定\N{\rEng}Yes. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你跑来这儿干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,送你个东西\N{\rEng}Brought you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\N{\rEng}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是...\N{\rEng}It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,给你那只鸟的新手套\N{\rEng}it's a new glove for your bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我有手套了\N{\rEng}I have a glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 别跑\N{\rEng}Agnes, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我认出你了\N{\rEng}I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那好 我是谁？\N{\rEng}Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 不算了解你 只是听到些传言...\N{\rEng}Well, I... I don't know you, but I've heard things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,说我是森林巫婆的女儿？\N{\rEng}I'm the daughter of a forest witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 村里这么说 但我 我不在意...\N{\rEng}Yes. People say that, but I-I don't care...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是我母亲的女儿\N{\rEng}I am my mother's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,从她那儿学的本事多着呢\N{\rEng}I've learnt many things from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞎看什么？\N{\rEng}What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看你 - 为什么？\N{\rEng}- You. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:12:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因... - 你这教书的 不该能言善辩吗？\N{\rEng}- I... - I thought you were a man of words, master tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还难住你了？ - 只是...\N{\rEng}- Are you not? - Jus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时很难直接跟人说话\N{\rEng}Speaking with people is sometimes difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那就讲个故事吧\N{\rEng}Well, tell me a story, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 讲故事？ - 对\N{\rEng}- A story? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你想听什么故事？\N{\rEng}What story would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,起码能打动你自己的故事\N{\rEng}Something that moves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道俄耳甫斯和欧律狄刻的故事吗？\N{\rEng}Do you know the story of Orpheus and Eurydice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.74,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 古希腊神话】
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,俄耳甫斯这个男人\N{\rEng}Orpheus is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有着天赋异禀的音乐才能\N{\rEng}a man of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他还有着天籁般的嗓音\N{\rEng}He has this exquisite voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他弹那种七弦里拉 是...\N{\rEng}His playing of the kithara, which is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是类似竖琴的乐器\N{\rEng}is-is a harp-like lyre,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,声音美得妙不可言\N{\rEng}is so divine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,连天上的鸟儿 地...\N{\rEng}birds, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,地上的走兽 甚 甚至石头和树\N{\rEng}the beasts, e-even the stones and the trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都能被他的音乐打动随之起舞\N{\rEng}they all moved to the rhythm of his music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,后来 俄耳甫斯爱上了一位美丽的山林少女 叫欧律狄刻\N{\rEng}Now, Orpheus falls in love with this beautiful nymph, Eurydice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和山林少女刚结完婚\N{\rEng}Soon after their marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她就被毒蛇咬了\N{\rEng}Eurydice's bitten by a viper
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,毒素在她体内迅速扩散\N{\rEng}and poison courses through her body,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她就此身亡\N{\rEng}and she's killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,俄耳甫斯悲痛欲绝\N{\rEng}And Orpheus, filled with grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下到冥府想要将她带回\N{\rEng}journeys to the underworld to take her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他用琴声迷住了守门的三头犬 刻耳柏洛斯\N{\rEng}He charms this three-headed dog, Cerberus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至感动了冥王哈得斯 最终...\N{\rEng}He beguiles Hades until finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,冥王同意了\N{\rEng}...he's allowed to take his love back with him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,允许把这名女子带回人间 但...\N{\rEng}to the world of the living but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一个条件\N{\rEng}...under one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什么条件？\N{\rEng}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这名女子必须跟在他身后\N{\rEng}She must follow behind him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而他绝对不能回头看\N{\rEng}and he must not turn around to look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 他们开始往人间走\N{\rEng}Now, as they begin their ascent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,俄耳甫斯却听不见他妻子的脚步声 于是他听啊...\N{\rEng}Orpheus can't hear her footsteps, so he listens...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,听啊 听啊 一直听\N{\rEng}...and listens and listens and listens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他只听得见自己的心跳\N{\rEng}But all he can hear is the sound of his heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,余下的只有沉寂\N{\rEng}And the rest is silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,当他快到冥门出口时\N{\rEng}And as he approaches the gates of the underworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他忍不住了\N{\rEng}...he can't contain himself any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他回头去看妻子 然后妻子...\N{\rEng}He turns around to look at her, and she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,永远被困在冥府里了\N{\rEng}...trapped in the underworld forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好故事\N{\rEng}That was a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗？\N{\rEng}Did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾草者 古之名药也\N{\rEng}Remember, mugwort, what you brought to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:19.85,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《九草咒》: 古英语药咒 列九种草药以驱毒治疫】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,世人皆知其德 传颂至今\N{\rEng}what you readied at Regenmeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,其名曰艾 为草之首\N{\rEng}You're called Una, the most ancient plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱三疾 能制三十疾\N{\rEng}You defy three, you defy 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,能解毒气 能散瘴疠\N{\rEng}you defy venom, you defy air illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能降瘟疫 克之而胜\N{\rEng}you defy the horror that stalks the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,车前草者 草之母也\N{\rEng}And you, waybread, plant mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,根植东方 性禀刚毅\N{\rEng}you're open to the east yet mighty within.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,遭车碾而不折 遇众踏而复起\N{\rEng}Carts creeped over you, women rode over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,刚柔相济 疗人间之疾苦\N{\rEng}You withstood it all, and you pushed back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的能靠摸一个人的手\N{\rEng}Is it true that you know everything about a person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看透一切吗？\N{\rEng}by touching them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,并非全部\N{\rEng}Not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你摸我时你看到了什么？\N{\rEng}When you touched me here, what did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见了一幅画面\N{\rEng}I saw a landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一幅画？ - 嗯\N{\rEng}- You saw a landscape? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,空洞 黑洞 裂口\N{\rEng}Spaces, caves, cliff tops,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,暗道和深海\N{\rEng}tunnels and oceans,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,深不见底 一片漆黑的虚空\N{\rEng}this deep, dark, black void,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,未知的国度\N{\rEng}undiscovered countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）天道有常 宿命有律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:21.30,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读《农事诗》第一卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）万物难逃衰落之数 消亡乃其必然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）天道有常 宿命有律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）万物难逃衰落之数 消亡乃其必然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她说话了...\N{\rEng}She speaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她说话了 她说话了\N{\rEng}She speaks, she speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,且慢\N{\rEng}But, soft,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那窗户透出来的是什么光？\N{\rEng}what light through yonder window breaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那是东方 朱丽叶就是太阳...\N{\rEng}It is the east, and Juliet is the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,赶走那....\N{\rEng}...and kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嫉妒的月亮\N{\rEng}...the envious moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.97,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在创作《罗密欧与朱丽叶》第二幕第二场】
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你成亲\N{\rEng}I wish to be handfasted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我 我必须和你成亲\N{\rEng}No, I... I must be handfasted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,非你不可\N{\rEng}No one else will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去跟你继母和你哥哥说\N{\rEng}I-I will speak with your stepmother and your brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,估计他们不会答应\N{\rEng}and of course they will not agree, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:18:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不管行不行就这么定了 不能等了\N{\rEng}I don't care because I have no talent for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是私定终身\N{\rEng}I cannot abide waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那你父母怎么办？\N{\rEng}What about your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们绝不会答应的\N{\rEng}Your parents will never agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\rEng}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等 等下\N{\rEng}Wait. Wait. W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跑不掉了 - 别\N{\rEng}- No! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手套\N{\rEng}My glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是我母亲留给我的 - 哦\N{\rEng}- This is my mother's glove. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她源于森林\N{\rEng}She came out of the woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就像她的母亲一样\N{\rEng}...like her mother
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,像她母亲的母亲一样\N{\rEng}and her mother before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我家族女人能看到些...\N{\rEng}The women in my family see things...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别人看不到的东西\N{\rEng}...that others don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艾草者 古之名药也\N{\rEng}Remember, mugwort,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,世人皆知其德 传颂至今\N{\rEng}what you brought to pass, what you readied at Regenmeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其名曰艾 为草之首\N{\rEng}You're called Una, the most ancient plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱三疾 能制三十疾\N{\rEng}You defy three, you defy 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能解毒气 能散瘴疠\N{\rEng}you defy venom, you defy air illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能降瘟疫 克之而胜\N{\rEng}you defy the horror that stalks the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,巴塞洛缪 会好的\N{\rEng}Bartholomew, it will heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,会留疤吗？\N{\rEng}Will it make a scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会 但并非坏事\N{\rEng}It may. That's no bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听\N{\rEng}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,听见了么？\N{\rEng}Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,留心你的梦 安妮丝\N{\rEng}You must pay attention to your dreams, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,梦永远会指引你\N{\rEng}They will always guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们好 - 你也好\N{\rEng}- Good day. - Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 你怎么在...\N{\rEng}Agnes, what's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在这儿？\N{\rEng}what's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她母亲把她逐出家门了\N{\rEng}Her mother has banished her from their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我生母 而且...\N{\rEng}She's not my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我家那房子归我哥哥巴塞洛缪\N{\rEng}The house belongs to my brother, Bartholomew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是自愿离开的\N{\rEng}I chose to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她有身孕了\N{\rEng}She's with child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还说孩子是你的\N{\rEng}Says it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗？真是你的吗？ - 呃...\N{\rEng}- Is it? Yours? - Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她肚子里的孩子 是你弄的吗？\N{\rEng}The child in her belly, did you put it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\rEng}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们已经私定了 娘 - 休想\N{\rEng}- We are handfasted, Mother. - We will never allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这有什么错啊 - 没我们的同意\N{\rEng}- There is no sin in it. - I'm afraid you will need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你成不了亲的 - 这有什么错啊\N{\rEng}- our consent, and we will... - There is no sin in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们决不允许这桩婚事 - 行 行\N{\rEng}- ...we will never give it, ever! - All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你被她蛊惑了 - 不是的\N{\rEng}- You've been bewitched. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿你当水手送命 也别娶这个巫婆\N{\rEng}I'd rather you went to sea than marry this wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\rEng}Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不必这样\N{\rEng}There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,既然他们两厢情愿 这事好解决\N{\rEng}I have no doubt we can come to an arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 约翰 - 安静 女人\N{\rEng}- John. - Hush, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定想在教堂里\N{\rEng}I am certain you are eager
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你妹妹出嫁吧\N{\rEng}to see your sister before the altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定想现在\N{\rEng}I'm certain you'd rather not see your boy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,控告你儿子奸淫\N{\rEng}dragged before the bawdy court.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要闹成那样\N{\rEng}There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都已经私定了\N{\rEng}They said they are handfasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁不嫁由我说了算\N{\rEng}Only if I say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁给那白面书生到底有啥好处？他有什么用\N{\rEng}But why marry a pasty-faced scholar? What use is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他的内心比我见过的任何人都深邃\N{\rEng}He's got more inside of him than any man I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.38,0:23:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,人心是会变的\N{\rEng}Everything will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你也不例外\N{\rEng}You. You will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心已经变了\N{\rEng}I'm already changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,里头太静了\N{\rEng}It's too quiet in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.81,0:23:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哪儿里头？\N{\rEng}In where?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们家\N{\rEng}That house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,记得我们害怕迷茫时 娘怎么劝咱的吗？\N{\rEng}What would our mother say to us if we were afraid or uncertain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要敞开心扉\N{\rEng}To live with our hearts open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫它躲在黑暗里\N{\rEng}To shut it not in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而是转向太阳\N{\rEng}but to turn it to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他爱的是我本色 不图我变成谁\N{\rEng}He loves me for what I am, not what I ought to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就嫁给他吧\N{\rEng}Then marry him you shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,艾草者 古之名药也\N{\rEng}Remember, mugwort...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,来 说跟我一起说 一起说\N{\rEng}Say it with me. Say it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,世人皆知其德\N{\rEng}What you brought to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,传颂至今\N{\rEng}what you readied at Regenmeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,其名曰艾 为草之首\N{\rEng}You are called Una, the most ancient plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱三疾 能制三十疾\N{\rEng}You defy three, you defy 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能解毒气 能散瘴疠\N{\rEng}you defy venom, you defy air illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.85,0:24:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能降瘟疫 克之而胜\N{\rEng}you defy the horror that stalks the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.33,0:24:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\N{\rEng}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.18,0:24:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\N{\rEng}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.73,0:27:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.49,0:28:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.11,0:28:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看 看那光 那是火\N{\rEng}Look. Look at that. Look at the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.98,0:29:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看看 那是什么啊\N{\rEng}Mmm, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.39,0:29:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是小狗叼进来的东西\N{\rEng}The doggy dragged something in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.36,0:29:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快看\N{\rEng}There's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.82,0:29:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.04,0:29:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你爹回来了\N{\rEng}Daddy's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.11,0:29:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,回来了\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.15,0:29:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,针脚要小一点\N{\rEng}Stitches need to be smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.26,0:29:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再小 再小一点\N{\rEng}M-Much smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.46,0:29:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.36,0:29:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哼\N{\rEng}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.68,0:29:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没出息\N{\rEng}Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.37,0:29:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好 再小点\N{\rEng}Okay, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.28,0:29:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再小点\N{\rEng}smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.30,0:30:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪儿？ - 我要出去\N{\rEng}- Where are you going? - I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.80,0:30:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,回去干活\N{\rEng}Get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.04,0:30:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你最后一次打我\N{\rEng}That was the last time you will ever hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.65,0:30:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\N{\rEng}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.18,0:30:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白吗？ - 明白\N{\rEng}- Do you understand?! - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.37,0:30:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,爱人 该睡觉了\N{\rEng}My love, you should come back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.96,0:30:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你在写什么？\N{\rEng}What are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.11,0:30:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不值一提\N{\rEng}Nothing of note.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.12,0:31:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,总有值得称道的地方\N{\rEng}It's never nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.67,0:31:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还没写好呢\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.31,0:31:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也许写完会好...\N{\rEng}Perhaps when it's finished, it will...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.29,0:31:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\rEng}Perhaps when it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.68,0:31:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,念给我听听吧\N{\rEng}Why don't you read me what you've written?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.09,0:31:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 这还没...\N{\rEng}A-Agnes, it's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.63,0:31:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还没写好呢\N{\rEng}It-It's not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.92,0:31:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没写好\N{\rEng}It's not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.96,0:31:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别敲了 吵醒孩子了\N{\rEng}Stop it. You'll wake the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.55,0:31:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.54,0:31:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不哭 不哭\N{\rEng}No. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.47,0:31:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.53,0:31:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝多了\N{\rEng}I've had too much, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.56,0:31:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 我喝多了\N{\rEng}Agnes, I've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.16,0:31:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝...\N{\rEng}I've had...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.51,0:32:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝的太多了\N{\rEng}I've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.41,0:32:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.15,0:32:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么心事吗？\N{\rEng}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.03,0:32:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你的手看看\N{\rEng}Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.71,0:32:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别 别 别 别\N{\rEng}Pl-Pl-Please, please, please, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.75,0:32:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别 求你了 别\N{\rEng}please, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.53,0:32:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怕我看见什么吗？ - 求你了 别\N{\rEng}- What are you afraid I will see? - Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.22,0:32:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕我将来会伤害你\N{\rEng}That I am a violent and dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.36,0:32:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 你不是那样的人\N{\rEng}No, you are none of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.77,0:32:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么能肯定？ - 你是个好人 你是个...\N{\rEng}- How do you know? - You're a good man. You're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.20,0:32:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好人\N{\rEng}You are a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.74,0:32:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好人\N{\rEng}You're a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.04,0:32:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是后悔跟我结婚了吗？\N{\rEng}Is it that you wish that we never wed?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.95,0:32:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能说出这种话？\N{\rEng}How could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.24,0:32:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能说出这种话？\N{\rEng}How could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.62,0:33:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我活着就是为了你和苏珊娜\N{\rEng}You and Susanna are all that I live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.89,0:33:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我活着就是为了你们\N{\rEng}All that I live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.70,0:33:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那到底怎么回事？ - 是...\N{\rEng}- What is it, then? - This...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.91,0:33:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 把手给我 - 停下\N{\rEng}- Here. Look at me. - Just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.88,0:33:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,停 停 求你停下 停 停 停\N{\rEng}Stop, stop. Please, please, please, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.76,0:33:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\rEng}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.31,0:33:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 听着 听我说\N{\rEng}Listen. Listen. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.37,0:33:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我迷失了\N{\rEng}I'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.92,0:33:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不...\N{\rEng}I've lost my...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.10,0:33:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到方向了\N{\rEng}I've lost my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.93,0:33:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要 我需要静下心好好写作 安妮丝\N{\rEng}I just need to-- uh, Agnes, I just need to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.82,0:33:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他都睡不着觉 \N{\rEng}He's not sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.61,0:33:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他对你发火了吗？ - 没有\N{\rEng}- Has he ever lost his temper with you? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.23,0:33:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 要是他对你动手.... - 没有 他从没那样 从没那样\N{\rEng}- If he raises a hand... - No, he has never. He's never.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.93,0:33:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是为自己懊恼\N{\rEng} He's angry with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.23,0:33:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,心里难受得要命\N{\rEng}He's sick with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.45,0:33:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好人\N{\rEng}He's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.72,0:33:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好丈夫 也是个好父亲\N{\rEng}He's a good husband, he's a good father,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.15,0:34:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但他还需要更多\N{\rEng}but he n-needs more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.05,0:34:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经有了家和你 还能需要什么？\N{\rEng}What could he possibly need other than his family and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.54,0:34:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他已经有了你 - 他需要去伦敦\N{\rEng}- He has you. - He needs to go to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.92,0:34:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伦敦？ - 是的\N{\rEng}- London? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.85,0:34:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥去伦敦？ \N{\rEng}Why London?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.72,0:34:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为伦敦汇聚天下\N{\rEng}Because London is where the whole world gathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.76,0:34:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定能把他爹的手艺带去发扬光大\N{\rEng}Perhaps he could extend his father's business there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.96,0:34:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哎 你又冲动了 - 谁知道他将来会怎样\N{\rEng}- Oh, you're being hasty again. - Who knows what he may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.60,0:34:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是冲动 他需要更多\N{\rEng}I'm not being hasty. He needs more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.31,0:34:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他只是太闲了 - 他不该呆这小地方\N{\rEng}- Well, he needs proper work. - He's not of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.27,0:34:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给他找个活儿忙起来\N{\rEng}The man needs proper work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.66,0:34:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这小地方能有什么出路？ -  他不能就这么跑掉\N{\rEng}- What's in this little town? - He can't just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.14,0:34:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这小日子 这小地方\N{\rEng}This little life? This little thing, it'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.94,0:34:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,会逼疯他的\N{\rEng}...crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.26,0:34:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他得离他爹远点\N{\rEng}He needs distance from his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.15,0:34:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他一起去伦敦吗？\N{\rEng}And you would go with him to London?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.43,0:34:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 等他安顿好再说\N{\rEng}No, I'll wait until he's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.32,0:34:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,马上家里就会多一口人\N{\rEng}There'll be more of us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.86,0:34:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 又怀上了？ - 是的\N{\rEng}- Another child? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.80,0:34:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,夏末时候生\N{\rEng}By summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.17,0:34:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那现在更不能把他送走了\N{\rEng}Then now is not the time to send him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.77,0:34:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那我会失去他的\N{\rEng}I'll lose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.07,0:34:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在失去他了\N{\rEng}I'm already losing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.52,0:34:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要是送他走 就彻底失去他了\N{\rEng}You'll lose him if you send him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.64,0:34:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不会的 我肯定我俩的爱能维系得住\N{\rEng}No, I know, I know that our love will keep us steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.15,0:34:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 替我跟他爹说说吧\N{\rEng}Please. Will you speak to his father?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.82,0:34:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你跟他提去伦敦的事 他会听你的\N{\rEng}He'll listen to you if you suggest him going to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.84,0:34:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.52,0:34:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我得找个住处\N{\rEng}I should find lodgings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.91,0:35:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,最好靠河的 离河边皮革场近点\N{\rEng}Be near the river, close to the tanneries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.44,0:35:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说那河水很急\N{\rEng}But I'm told that the currents in the river are dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.13,0:35:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,过河要请有经验的船夫\N{\rEng}and that you must engage an experienced boatman
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.21,0:35:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,每次过河我都照办\N{\rEng}every time you cross, and I'll be certain to do that every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.53,0:35:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\rEng}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.11,0:35:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会时时刻刻\N{\rEng}And I will think of you and Susanna
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.73,0:35:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,挂念你和苏珊娜的\N{\rEng}with every passing moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.26,0:35:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给咱们找个好住处\N{\rEng}And I will find us lodgings in London,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.84,0:35:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候在伦敦团聚\N{\rEng}and we shall all be together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.83,0:35:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没预见出是男孩还是女孩吗？\N{\rEng}Do you still not know if it's a boy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.07,0:35:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.21,0:35:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也说不清为什么\N{\rEng}Don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.54,0:35:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说过会有两个孩子陪你到最后吗？\N{\rEng}Have you not said that you would always have two children?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.48,0:35:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.08,0:35:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,临终前会有两个孩子在身边\N{\rEng}Two children at my deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.90,0:35:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,第二个能陪你到最后的人来了\N{\rEng}Well, then, here is the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.96,0:35:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们就别道别了 - 好\N{\rEng}- We won't say goodbye. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.91,0:36:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别磨蹭了 快走吧\N{\rEng}You get-- Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.42,0:36:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要出门吗？ - 不是 我只是...\N{\rEng}- You going somewhere? - No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.99,0:36:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我要去湖边走走...\N{\rEng}Yes, I'm going to the lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.94,0:36:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你不许进森林\N{\rEng}You're not going to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.61,0:36:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我非去不可 - 不 你不许去 吉尔伯特快来\N{\rEng}- I must. - No, you must not. Gilbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.03,0:36:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你得让我去那里\N{\rEng}You... you have to let me go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.08,0:36:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你必须让我走 - 听我说 安妮丝\N{\rEng}- Let me go there! - Listen Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.10,0:36:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你得放我去 - 河堤已经决口了\N{\rEng}- You must let me go! - The river has burst its banks!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.64,0:36:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我去 - 外面很危险\N{\rEng}- Let me! - There is no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.88,0:36:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 根本没路去森林那边 - 放我走 不要\N{\rEng}- There's no way to get to the forest. - Let me! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.73,0:36:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们都为你准备好了 - 我孩子\N{\rEng}- We have everything ready for you. - My baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.38,0:37:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我 我孩子\N{\rEng}No, my-my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.47,0:37:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\N{\rEng}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.21,0:37:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,生不出来\N{\rEng}It isn't coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.45,0:37:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法在这屋里生孩子\N{\rEng}I will not have my baby in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.90,0:37:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没法在这屋\N{\rEng}Not in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.51,0:37:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没法\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.11,0:37:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,河水\N{\rEng}The river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.36,0:37:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 使劲儿 使劲儿 使劲儿 - 不 不 不\N{\rEng}- Hush, hush, hush, hush. Hush. - No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.76,0:37:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他说要住河边\N{\rEng}He spoke about the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.99,0:37:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,河很危险 他可能会被冲走\N{\rEng}The river is dangerous. He may be swept downstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.35,0:37:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.71,0:37:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 安妮丝 他一切安好\N{\rEng}Agnes. Agnes, all is well with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.75,0:37:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道忘了他最近的信吗？\N{\rEng}Do you not recall his last letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.93,0:37:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫了\N{\rEng}Stop the screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.07,0:37:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,会把整村人都吵醒的\N{\rEng}You'll wake the whole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.28,0:37:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他语气...\N{\rEng}He sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.41,0:37:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他语气不对\N{\rEng}He sounded different.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.03,0:37:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他带来的是好消息\N{\rEng}No, he had good news for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.24,0:37:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 剧院 - 剧院\N{\rEng}- The theater. - Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.54,0:37:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他和剧团定下来了\N{\rEng}He has a contract with the players
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.99,0:37:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做剧院用的手套 - 剧院\N{\rEng}- to make gloves for the theater. - the theater
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.55,0:38:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 使劲儿\N{\rEng}Agnes, hush now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.47,0:38:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,使劲儿 使劲儿 使劲儿\N{\rEng}Hush. Hush. Hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.87,0:38:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,用力 用力\N{\rEng}Bear down. Bear down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.14,0:38:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 来了\N{\rEng}Ah! Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.22,0:38:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 出来了 - 是个男孩\N{\rEng}- There we go. - It's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.08,0:38:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真好\N{\rEng}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.39,0:38:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子 乖孩子\N{\rEng}Good boy. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.02,0:38:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是个男孩\N{\rEng}It's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.29,0:38:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是个男孩\N{\rEng}It's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.66,0:38:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子\N{\rEng}My boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.52,0:38:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.36,0:38:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？怎么了？\N{\rEng}What is it? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.50,0:38:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她又要生了\N{\rEng}She's starting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.69,0:38:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 姑娘啊 你怀的是双胞胎 - 来 伊莱莎\N{\rEng}- You're having twins, my girl. - Come on, Eliza.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.89,0:38:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快 抱着他\N{\rEng}Here. Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.38,0:39:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,抱好\N{\rEng}Take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.67,0:39:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\N{\rEng}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.10,0:39:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我临终前会有两个孩子在身边\N{\rEng}Two standing at my deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.97,0:39:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为...\N{\rEng}I always believed that it would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.90,0:39:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以为是长大的孩子\N{\rEng}that they would be my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.94,0:39:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我...\N{\rEng}And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.67,0:39:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了 原来就是你们俩\N{\rEng}now I see it will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.43,0:39:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,得把你扶到产凳上\N{\rEng}We need to get you to the stool.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.78,0:39:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快生了 要生了\N{\rEng}It's coming. It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.16,0:39:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要 - 来 来 起来 起来\N{\rEng}- No. - Come on. Come on up. Up, up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.33,0:39:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别 我 我不行\N{\rEng}Please. I can't... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.45,0:39:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\N{\rEng}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.68,0:39:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 - 我不该...\N{\rEng}- Go. - I should never have...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.72,0:39:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了...\N{\rEng}I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.74,0:39:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺不过去了\N{\rEng}I can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.19,0:39:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我弄错了 我弄错了\N{\rEng}I got it wrong. I got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.08,0:39:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我弄错...\N{\rEng}I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.38,0:39:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他不在\N{\rEng}He... He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.82,0:39:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他不在这里\N{\rEng}He's... He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.08,0:39:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 你能行的\N{\rEng}Agnes, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.38,0:39:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须行\N{\rEng}and you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.25,0:39:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\N{\rEng}I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.02,0:39:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.38,0:39:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你能行的\N{\rEng}You can...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.17,0:39:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你会挺过去的\N{\rEng}and you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.06,0:40:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫就在这间屋里出生\N{\rEng}Your husband was born here in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.44,0:40:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在那窗边 第一次呼吸\N{\rEng}He took his first breath there by the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.03,0:40:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.19,0:40:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 保住孩子\N{\rEng}Please let this child live.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.08,0:40:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一定保孩子 一定\N{\rEng}Let this child live. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.95,0:40:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让他...\N{\rEng}Will you let him...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.63,0:40:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让他回到家后能有孩子陪他\N{\rEng}Let him come back and be with his child.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.50,0:40:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.96,0:40:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让他对我留个好念想\N{\rEng}Let him think kindly of me always.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.45,0:40:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,记着我\N{\rEng}Remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.07,0:40:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\N{\rEng}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.36,0:40:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\N{\rEng}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.70,0:40:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,娘？\N{\rEng}Mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.39,0:40:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她没抗住\N{\rEng}Just too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.19,0:40:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她承受了很大的痛苦\N{\rEng}She was in too much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.36,0:40:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太可怜了\N{\rEng}I mean, poor woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.70,0:40:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越痛 她承受不住了\N{\rEng}She just got weaker and weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.96,0:40:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候命就是这样\N{\rEng}I mean, that's just the way of it sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.48,0:40:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她 她大概早就知道这一刻了\N{\rEng}She-she must have known the end was nigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.22,0:40:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,最好别跟孩子提起她了\N{\rEng}Best not speak of her to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.10,0:40:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,再娶一个吧\N{\rEng}Safer with a different mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.60,0:41:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子都还小\N{\rEng}So young.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.64,0:41:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,兴许能忘掉\N{\rEng}They may not remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.74,0:41:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘啊 - 安妮丝 安妮丝\N{\rEng}- Mum! - Agnes. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.51,0:41:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘啊 不 - 不 不 安妮丝\N{\rEng}- Mama, no! - No, no. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.46,0:41:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子 孩子\N{\rEng}Child. Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.85,0:41:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘 不要 - 不 不 孩子 孩子 不行\N{\rEng}- Mummy, no! - No, no, no. Ch-Ch-Ch-- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.25,0:41:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放开我 - 不行\N{\rEng}- No! - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.47,0:41:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 让我见娘 - 不 不\N{\rEng}- No, let me see her! - No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.56,0:41:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要见娘 - 不\N{\rEng}- Let me see her! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.24,0:41:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 娘\N{\rEng}No, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.88,0:41:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安妮丝 - 不\N{\rEng}- Agnes. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.95,0:41:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,娘 我要我娘 我要我娘\N{\rEng}Mum. I want, I want my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.81,0:41:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我娘啊...\N{\rEng}I want my mum...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.65,0:41:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 是个女孩\N{\rEng}Oh! Here we go! It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.54,0:41:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是个女孩 她...\N{\rEng}It's a girl. She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.91,0:42:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等... - 怎么了？\N{\rEng}- It's... Wait. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.59,0:42:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\N{\rEng}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.85,0:42:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么不哭？\N{\rEng}Why is she not crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.90,0:42:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么不哭？\N{\rEng}Why is she not crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.79,0:42:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她没活过来\N{\rEng}She lives not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.65,0:42:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让我抱抱\N{\rEng}Let me have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.67,0:42:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 这不吉利\N{\rEng}You should not look upon her. It's bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.49,0:42:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把她给我\N{\rEng}Give her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.48,0:42:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把她安葬妥当的\N{\rEng}I'll make sure it gets a decent burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.68,0:42:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把我孩子给我\N{\rEng}Give me my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.69,0:42:25.10,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【双胞胎: 当时双胞胎被视为怪异现象和不祥征兆】
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.11,0:42:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子啊\N{\rEng}My child.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.62,0:42:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 你有个儿子\N{\rEng}Agnes, you have a baby boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.24,0:42:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他抱来 你可以喂他\N{\rEng}Let me bring him to you, and you may feed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.98,0:42:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩已经去了天国\N{\rEng}The girl has gone to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.98,0:42:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会去天国的\N{\rEng}She's not gone to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.86,0:42:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲去世那晚我发过誓\N{\rEng}I made a vow the night my mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.25,0:42:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去你们的教堂 但别指望我开口说什么\N{\rEng}I will go to your church, but I shan't say a word there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.25,0:42:57.11,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 当时无宗教自由 故以含蓄方式表达不信教】
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.34,0:43:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 太好了 太好了\N{\rEng}Yes. Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.72,0:43:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下去的\N{\rEng}You will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.56,0:43:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下去的\N{\rEng}You will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.53,0:43:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保护你到底 绝不放手\N{\rEng}I will make sure nothing ever takes you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.63,0:44:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么都找不到\N{\rEng}I actually couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.00,0:44:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.29,0:44:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\N{\rEng}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.61,0:44:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rEng}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.94,0:44:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,找到帽子了\N{\rEng}I found my hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.18,0:44:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来 对\N{\rEng}Okay. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.47,0:44:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来 转过去 转过去\N{\rEng}Okay, take that side. Take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.70,0:45:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.14,0:45:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后系好\N{\rEng}And put it around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.55,0:45:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,完美\N{\rEng}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.25,0:45:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哎呀 - 我来吧\N{\rEng}- Ooh. Sorry. - Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.57,0:45:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,挡到我脸了\N{\rEng}It's down my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.09,0:45:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟我学“我是哈姆奈特” - “我是哈姆奈特”\N{\rEng}- I'm Hamnet. - I'm Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.13,0:45:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- “我是珠迪丝” - “我是珠迪丝”\N{\rEng}- I'm Judith. - I'm Judith.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.88,0:45:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,屋里不准跑\N{\rEng}There will be no running in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.46,0:45:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要举止端正 要像...\N{\rEng}Conduct yourselves, please, as...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.20,0:45:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,淑女与绅士\N{\rEng}gentlewomen and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.39,0:45:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪儿？\N{\rEng}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.82,0:45:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对 他来了 他来了\N{\rEng}Yeah. He's-he's coming. He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.50,0:45:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,回来了\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.59,0:45:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.48,0:45:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一看就知道他俩对调了衣服\N{\rEng}We all know they've swapped clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.63,0:46:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们什么时候揭穿？\N{\rEng}How long are we going to pretend we don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.42,0:46:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他们继续演 咱们就不揭穿\N{\rEng}We'll pretend for as long as they think they're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.64,0:46:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.25,0:46:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,爹 能再教我下\N{\rEng}Father, will you help me with the Greek passage
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.08,0:46:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天那段希腊文吗？\N{\rEng}from yesterday's lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.77,0:46:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 你不是会背了吗？\N{\rEng}Hamnet, I thought you'd already learnt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.28,0:46:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了 因为把课本落学堂了\N{\rEng}I didn't because I left my primer at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.95,0:46:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 哈姆奈特\N{\rEng}Well, Hamnet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.45,0:46:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你要用心学\N{\rEng}you need to take your studies seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.77,0:46:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不努力怎么会进步...\N{\rEng}How do you expect to improve if you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.15,0:46:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,（希腊语）吾不肯苟且而生 不甘平庸而逝
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.15,0:46:29.57,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读荷马《伊利亚特》第22卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.57,0:46:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,（希腊语）愿成就丰功伟绩 令后世永传吾名
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.57,0:46:34.61,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《伊利亚特》: 荷马(古希腊诗人)史诗 论英雄 战争与命运】
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.38,0:46:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群小淘气\N{\rEng}You rascals.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.82,0:46:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们耍到你了吗？ - 当然了\N{\rEng}- Did we trick you? - Of course you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.55,0:46:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们又互换来耍我\N{\rEng}You swapped places to hoodwink me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.12,0:46:45.79,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 当时女性普遍无法接受正规教育 现实中他妻女都不识字】
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.80,0:46:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜 过来\N{\rEng}Susanna, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.14,0:46:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来\N{\rEng}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.25,0:46:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还记得要给娘准备的那件事吗？\N{\rEng}Now, do you remember the thing we were going to do for your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.10,0:46:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 都记得吗？准备好了吗？\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - You remember? You ready to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.61,0:46:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 好 快去 快去准备\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - Okay. Go outside quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.39,0:47:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快去 快去 快去\N{\rEng}Go, go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.99,0:47:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 朝前走 - 别急\N{\rEng}- Just step toward... - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.64,0:47:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再走 往右走 小心\N{\rEng}One st-- Come to your right. Step.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.96,0:47:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点 再迈一步\N{\rEng}Step. One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.29,0:47:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啥 - 再迈一步\N{\rEng}- What. - One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.40,0:47:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们三个儿啥时候再聚？\N{\rEng}When shall we three meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.39,0:47:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等打雷 等闪电 还是等下雨？\N{\rEng}In thunder, lightning or in rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.60,0:47:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等到这场吵闹都停了 等到这一仗打出个输赢了\N{\rEng}When hurly-burly's done, when the battle's lost and won!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.96,0:47:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那就在太阳落山以前\N{\rEng}That will be ere at set of sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.65,0:47:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在什么地方？ - 就在荒原\N{\rEng}- Where the place? - Upon the heath.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.32,0:47:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿同安妮丝会面\N{\rEng}There to meet with Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.33,0:47:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 灰妖猫\N{\rEng}I come, Graymalkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.92,0:47:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤蟆叫\N{\rEng}Paddock calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.84,0:47:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,马上到\N{\rEng}Anon!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.58,0:47:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,美即是丑 丑即是美\N{\rEng}Fair is foul and foul is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.50,0:47:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,美即是丑 丑即是美 美即是丑 丑即是美\N{\rEng}Fair is foul and foul is fair. Fair is foul and foul is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.87,0:47:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,美即是丑 丑即是美\N{\rEng}Fair is foul and foul is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.87,0:47:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,穿入到...\N{\rEng}Hover through the...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.88,0:47:54.36,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《麦克白》: 出自第一幕第一场 参考卞之琳译本】
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.37,0:47:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,演得好\N{\rEng}Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.45,0:47:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真精彩\N{\rEng}That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.80,0:48:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,挖深点 把土拨到一边\N{\rEng}Dig it deep, and then you move all of it to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.33,0:48:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把根放进去\N{\rEng}and then you put it down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.28,0:48:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吧 然后把土填回去\N{\rEng}Right? And then you get the soil around the sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.41,0:48:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,用手把土拍平\N{\rEng}and then you pat it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.24,0:48:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后手上就沾了土\N{\rEng}And then you get bits like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.49,0:48:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,然后两手搓一搓\N{\rEng}And you rub it in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.87,0:48:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 向后退\N{\rEng}Whoa. And then back!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.38,0:48:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,照我这样做\N{\rEng}Do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.77,0:48:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后转圈 盯住对手\N{\rEng}And when you're doing this, circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.28,0:48:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对 就是这样\N{\rEng}Yeah, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.12,0:48:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？\N{\rEng}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.88,0:48:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,前进 后撤\N{\rEng}Forward. And back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.73,0:48:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 挡剑 挡剑 挡剑\N{\rEng}Now, parry, parry, parry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.95,0:48:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 再来\N{\rEng}Good. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.43,0:48:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,接着 我出这招\N{\rEng}Now, after that one, I'm gonna do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.83,0:48:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你要闪开\N{\rEng}and you get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.09,0:48:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？绕圈走 转动你的剑\N{\rEng}Ready? Circle off. Spin your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.29,0:48:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不对\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.61,0:48:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,绕圈 把剑转起来\N{\rEng}Circle, spin your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.20,0:48:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 向前迈\N{\rEng}Now, come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.70,0:48:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再往后退\N{\rEng}And go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.12,0:48:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,挡剑三次\N{\rEng}One, two three.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.03,0:48:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,闪开\N{\rEng}Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.27,0:48:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好 再来一次\N{\rEng}Very good. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.57,0:48:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝 闻闻这是什么？\N{\rEng}Judith, what's this one called?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.21,0:48:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 百里香 百里香 - 是迷迭香\N{\rEng}- Thyme. Thyme. - Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.46,0:48:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是百里香 - 好吧 百里香 百里香\N{\rEng}-Thyme. - Thyme. Thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.22,0:49:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我记错了 - 没关系\N{\rEng}- I got it mixed up. - That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.28,0:49:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这株是...\N{\rEng}This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.75,0:49:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是迷迭香 - 对\N{\rEng}- Now, that's rosemary. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.07,0:49:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,迷迭香有什么用处？\N{\rEng}And what is rosemary for?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.84,0:49:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放在苹果里一起炖 - 炖苹果\N{\rEng}- Putting it in apples. - Apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.89,0:49:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 再闻闻\N{\rEng}No. What is Rosemary's for?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.52,0:49:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 记忆 - 纪念\N{\rEng}- Remembering. - Remembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.78,0:49:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对 记忆纪念\N{\rEng}Remembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.09,0:49:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 搓一搓\N{\rEng}Now, you're to rub all this in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.77,0:50:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,吹个小心愿进去\N{\rEng}You blow a little wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.32,0:50:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,许个愿 让他带走\N{\rEng}To wish him on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.74,0:50:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？这就是你和他的小秘密了\N{\rEng}Yeah? And it's your secret with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.97,0:50:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.35,0:50:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没看见他在天上吗？\N{\rEng}Did you not see him in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.06,0:50:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好 再来一次\N{\rEng}All right, do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.20,0:50:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再许个愿\N{\rEng}Make another wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.75,0:50:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看 就在上面\N{\rEng}Look. Right up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.26,0:50:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那里 看见了吗？\N{\rEng}Look, just there. Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.88,0:50:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他把你们所有的愿望都藏在他的小心窝里了\N{\rEng}And he's got all your wishes tucked in his little heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.25,0:50:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,每当想念他的时候\N{\rEng}So any time that you want to remember him,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.76,0:50:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要吹一下...\N{\rEng}you just have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.33,0:50:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿？\N{\rEng}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.83,0:50:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我要抓到你\N{\rEng}Huh? I'm gonna catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.99,0:50:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要抓到你\N{\rEng}I'm gonna catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.47,0:51:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爹？\N{\rEng}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.59,0:51:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？\N{\rEng}Is all well?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.41,0:51:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.84,0:51:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 别太靠近你爷爷\N{\rEng}Listen, I want you to stay away from your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.06,0:51:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会打你姐妹 但我担心你 \N{\rEng}He'll not hit your sisters, but it's you that I worry for,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.57,0:51:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,当我走了你要能保护好自己\N{\rEng}and I need to know that you'll be safe when I'm not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.22,0:51:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,又要回伦敦了么？\N{\rEng}You're going back to London again?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.34,0:51:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对 明天\N{\rEng}Yes, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.74,0:51:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,明天就走？\N{\rEng}Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.37,0:51:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\rEng}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.29,0:51:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我们能跟你一起去吗？\N{\rEng}Will we go with you this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.18,0:51:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 还不行\N{\rEng}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.68,0:51:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.38,0:51:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想念你的\N{\rEng}I'll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.02,0:51:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但我得走 你明白吗？我得...\N{\rEng}But I have to go, you understand? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.40,0:51:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.40,0:51:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\rEng}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.74,0:51:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\rEng}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.46,0:51:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你要替我照顾好你娘和你姐妹\N{\rEng}'Cause I need you to look after your mother and your sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.85,0:51:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,能做到吗？\N{\rEng}Will you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.29,0:51:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,能\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.71,0:52:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能做个男子汉吗？ - 能\N{\rEng}- Will you be brave? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.29,0:52:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？\N{\rEng}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.16,0:52:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你勇敢吗？ - 是\N{\rEng}- Will you be brave? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.18,0:52:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是男子汉吗？\N{\rEng}Will you be brave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.00,0:52:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗？ - 是 是 我是男子汉\N{\rEng}- Huh?! - Yes! Yes, I'll be brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.12,0:52:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢 我是男子汉\N{\rEng}I'll be brave. I'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.97,0:52:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经在伦敦替咱们物色好房子了\N{\rEng}I've looked at houses for us in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.14,0:52:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 秋天就要来了 - 嗯\N{\rEng}-Autumn is coming. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.51,0:52:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们会生病的\N{\rEng}And the children will fall ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.97,0:52:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝还是太虚弱了\N{\rEng}Judith, she's still not strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.00,0:52:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她常常胸闷\N{\rEng}She often gets congestion in her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.60,0:52:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦那空气...\N{\rEng}And the air in London is...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.12,0:52:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,去不了\N{\rEng}We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.95,0:52:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但迟早有一天 我们会去的\N{\rEng}But one day soon, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.73,0:52:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会跟你去伦敦的\N{\rEng}We will come to London with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.27,0:52:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的\N{\rEng}No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.03,0:52:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不会来的\N{\rEng}You'll never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.94,0:52:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天你嫌太热\N{\rEng}You've waited for the heat of summer to pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.29,0:52:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,秋天干燥\N{\rEng}...the dryness of autumn,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.56,0:53:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天太冷\N{\rEng}the snow and the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.10,0:53:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你压根儿不信珠迪丝能在伦敦活着\N{\rEng}You do not believe that Judith will ever survive London.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.90,0:53:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你会想尽一切办法保住那孩子\N{\rEng}You'd do anything in your power to keep that child alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.37,0:53:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,做母亲的不就该这样吗？\N{\rEng}Isn't that what a mother is supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.36,0:53:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是\N{\rEng}Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.53,0:53:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...\N{\rEng}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.28,0:53:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定就在这镇子附近给咱们找个家\N{\rEng}...I've decided to look for land outside Stratford.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.25,0:53:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你和孩子们还在斯特拉特福镇这片生活\N{\rEng}That's where you should live with the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.25,0:53:31.90,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【斯特拉特福: 距离伦敦160公里 当时为羊毛 皮革等畜产品加工地】
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.90,0:53:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你 - 嗯\N{\rEng}- Thank you. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.02,0:53:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.08,0:53:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来 啊\N{\rEng}Where is she? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.63,0:53:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特呢 你来了\N{\rEng}Hamnet. There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.54,0:53:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,过来吧\N{\rEng}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.45,0:54:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你 爱你 爱你\N{\rEng}I love you. I love you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.29,0:54:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 来亲一下\N{\rEng}All right. Love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.63,0:54:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 - 亲一下\N{\rEng}- Come on. - Love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.08,0:54:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,亲一下\N{\rEng}Love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.04,0:54:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.97,0:54:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 过来\N{\rEng}All right. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.15,0:54:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还记得我告诉你的话吗？ - 记得\N{\rEng}- Remember what I told you, okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.63,0:54:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子\N{\rEng}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.13,0:54:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要走了 - 再见\N{\rEng}- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.36,0:54:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 走了 - 再见\N{\rEng}- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.23,0:54:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真走了 - 再见\N{\rEng}- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.80,0:55:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 哈姆奈特？\N{\rEng}Hamnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.15,0:55:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 到这儿来\N{\rEng}Come on. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.66,0:55:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,把手给我\N{\rEng}Show me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.63,0:55:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你看到什么了？\N{\rEng}What? What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.22,0:55:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你...\N{\rEng}I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.03,0:55:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,长大了\N{\rEng}Grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.30,0:55:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,身强力壮\N{\rEng}And very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.92,0:55:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我还看到你在伦敦 和你父亲一起工作\N{\rEng}And I see you in London working with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.46,0:55:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在剧院吗？ - 对\N{\rEng}- In the theater? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.52,0:55:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在剧场\N{\rEng}At the playhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.99,0:55:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在那儿做什么？\N{\rEng}What will I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.73,0:55:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做什么呢？\N{\rEng}What do you wish to do, Hamnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.77,0:55:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想当个拿剑的演员\N{\rEng}I should be one of the players with a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.80,0:55:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拿剑的？\N{\rEng}A sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.42,0:55:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.71,0:55:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想拿剑和其他演员交锋\N{\rEng}And I shall clash it against the sword of the other player.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.50,0:56:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,示范给我看看\N{\rEng}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.03,0:56:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,会有场激烈的战斗\N{\rEng}There'll be a terrible fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.77,0:56:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,观众看得心惊胆战\N{\rEng}and everybody watching will be frightened out of their wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.68,0:56:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那谁会赢呢？\N{\rEng}And who will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.48,0:56:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,自然是我\N{\rEng}I shall, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.04,0:56:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是你\N{\rEng}Of course you shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.81,0:56:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,它们被什么惊到了\N{\rEng}Something has upset them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.05,0:56:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.31,0:56:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是天气\N{\rEng}The weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.98,0:56:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,或者空气里有什么 不确定\N{\rEng}Something in the air, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.91,0:56:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉琼今天别让孩子们出门了\N{\rEng}Best tell Joan to keep the children inside today.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.76,0:59:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝？\N{\rEng}Judith?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.14,0:59:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝？\N{\rEng}Judith?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.11,0:59:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿呢？\N{\rEng}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.81,0:59:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒啊\N{\rEng}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.15,0:59:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,面包师的猫生小猫咪了\N{\rEng}The baker told me her cat had kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.91,0:59:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们得去看看\N{\rEng}We need to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.42,0:59:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有八只呢 珠迪丝 八只\N{\rEng}There's eight, Judith. Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.55,1:00:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,得抓紧了 要下雨了\N{\rEng}We need to hurry. It's going to rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.60,1:00:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝？\N{\rEng}Judith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.57,1:00:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小珠？\N{\rEng}Jude?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.25,1:00:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？\N{\rEng}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.79,1:00:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哪儿不舒服？珠迪丝\N{\rEng}What's wrong, Judith?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.39,1:00:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你说话啊 珠迪丝\N{\rEng}Judith, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.62,1:00:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,起来啊\N{\rEng}Judith, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.60,1:00:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 珠迪丝 说句话\N{\rEng}Judith, please. Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.06,1:00:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了？ - 是珠迪丝\N{\rEng}- What is it? - It's Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.15,1:00:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她这样多久了？\N{\rEng}How long has she been like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.46,1:00:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我从学堂回来她就这样了\N{\rEng}Since I returned from school.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.54,1:00:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.70,1:00:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她得上了\N{\rEng}She's got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.55,1:01:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是？\N{\rEng}Hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.23,1:01:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她得了瘟疫\N{\rEng}She's got the pestilence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.89,1:01:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是 娘？\N{\rEng}Hasn't she, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.67,1:01:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,去找你奶奶\N{\rEng}Go find your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.06,1:01:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让她马上来\N{\rEng}Bid her to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.54,1:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快去\N{\rEng}Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.56,1:01:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她烧得厉害\N{\rEng}She's burning up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.61,1:01:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,得要水 要很多水\N{\rEng}We need, um, more water.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.03,1:01:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,烧大火 把水烧热了\N{\rEng}Make a bigger fire and heat up more water.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.79,1:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 需要热水 - 伊莱莎 去打些水来\N{\rEng}- We need warm water. - Eliza, fetch more water
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.02,1:01:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,把厨房的白雏菊也拿来\N{\rEng}and bring the Bellis from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.22,1:01:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,再拿肉桂\N{\rEng}A row of cinnamon.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.74,1:01:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,肉桂能退烧\N{\rEng}Cinnamon, that's good for drawing out the heat.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.94,1:01:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还要松草或者芸香 百里香也要\N{\rEng}Pineweed or a rue. Thyme, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.58,1:01:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去屋里找\N{\rEng}You'll find them in the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.13,1:01:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 娘啊 - 屋里那张桌子边 桌子边\N{\rEng}- Mama. Yeah. - The other table. The other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.55,1:01:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿呢 我的心肝\N{\rEng}Yeah, Mama's here, my love.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.94,1:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来 喝这个 迷迭香熬的药膏\N{\rEng}Here, drink this. It's rosemary and jelly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.38,1:01:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,会没事的 听到没\N{\rEng}All will be well, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.98,1:01:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,都会没事的\N{\rEng}All will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.30,1:01:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝 坚持住\N{\rEng}Judith, stay with.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.38,1:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿 没事的 娘在这儿\N{\rEng}Mama's here. It's okay. Mama's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.42,1:01:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大黄 得要大黄 能清肠子\N{\rEng}Rhubarb. We need rhubarb to purge the stomach,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.20,1:01:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,能驱瘟疫\N{\rEng}drive out the pestilence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.21,1:01:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你能去取吗？\N{\rEng}Can you go and fetch some?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.53,1:01:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿 没事的 珠迪丝 大家都在\N{\rEng}Mama's here. It's okay. Judith, we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.78,1:01:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜 你也去打些水来\N{\rEng}Susanna, draw some water, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.30,1:01:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特和玛丽还有苏珊娜\N{\rEng}Hamnet and... and Mary and Susanna.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.09,1:01:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快去打水\N{\rEng}Draw water as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.81,1:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么还没来呢？\N{\rEng}Why isn't he here?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.66,1:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱莎 去给你哥哥威廉写信 让他赶快回来\N{\rEng}Eliza, go write to your brother and tell him to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.78,1:02:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝\N{\rEng}Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.31,1:02:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,张开嘴 珠迪丝\N{\rEng}Open your mouth, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.57,1:02:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,张开嘴 娘在这儿 对 很好\N{\rEng}Open your mouth. Mama's here. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.65,1:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子\N{\rEng}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.31,1:02:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对 会没事的\N{\rEng}Yes, you'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.35,1:02:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,张开嘴 都喝下去\N{\rEng}You'll open your mouth. Drink it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.76,1:02:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喝下去 娘在这儿 别怕 珠迪丝\N{\rEng}Swallow it down. Mama's here. It's okay, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.33,1:02:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿 别怕\N{\rEng}Mama's here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.60,1:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.63,1:02:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.99,1:03:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.97,1:03:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经尽力了\N{\rEng}You have done all that you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.32,1:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不会放手的\N{\rEng}I will not let her cross over.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.82,1:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 你失去的三个女儿...\N{\rEng}Grandmama, you had three daughters that were taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.97,1:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也是像...\N{\rEng}Were they...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.55,1:03:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也是像珠迪丝这样吗？\N{\rEng}Were they like Judith?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.36,1:03:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮那时七岁\N{\rEng}Anne was seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.39,1:03:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,另两个还只是吃奶的婴儿\N{\rEng}The other two were just babies.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.06,1:03:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,都长了肿块...\N{\rEng}They all had swellings and...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.06,1:03:50.43,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【腺鼠疫: 会导致淋巴结肿大 常见于颈部 腋下和腹股沟】
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.44,1:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都发高烧 跟珠迪丝一样\N{\rEng}...fever like Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.94,1:03:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你娘在...\N{\rEng}Your mother's trying to...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.52,1:03:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拼命想保住她的孩子\N{\rEng}keep a grip on her child.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.50,1:04:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的\N{\rEng}It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.62,1:04:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,命是天给的 随时都能被收回\N{\rEng}What is given may be taken away at any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.90,1:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得时刻提防着\N{\rEng}We must never let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.72,1:04:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别把孩子们的...\N{\rEng}Never take for granted...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.83,1:04:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次心跳...\N{\rEng}...that our children's hearts beat,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.31,1:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次呼吸...\N{\rEng}that they draw breath,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.95,1:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的行走 说话...\N{\rEng}that they walk and speak and...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.29,1:04:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,欢笑 吵闹和嬉戏当作理所当然的\N{\rEng}...smile, argue, play.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.36,1:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,得时刻提醒自己 他们可能说没就没了\N{\rEng}Never forget for a moment that they may be gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.42,1:04:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹\N{\rEng}Jude.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.68,1:05:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小珠\N{\rEng}Jude.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.60,1:05:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别难过\N{\rEng}Don't be sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.74,1:05:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你要替我好好活下去\N{\rEng}You shall be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.80,1:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\rEng}I shall not.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.19,1:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你我活不下去\N{\rEng}Not without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.52,1:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,它来了\N{\rEng}It's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.14,1:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹 你看得到吗？\N{\rEng}Do you see it, Jude?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.43,1:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它在看着咱们呢\N{\rEng}It's watching us.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.75,1:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告诉它把咱们都带走\N{\rEng}I'll tell it to take us both.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.11,1:06:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要走一起走\N{\rEng}We'll go together.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.69,1:06:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,转过去\N{\rEng}Turn away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.08,1:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,转过去\N{\rEng}Turn away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.22,1:06:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它会看错的\N{\rEng}It'll make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.42,1:06:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它分不出咱俩谁是谁\N{\rEng}It can't tell us apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.04,1:06:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起呼吸 珠迪丝\N{\rEng}Breathe with me, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.20,1:07:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我把我的命给你\N{\rEng}I give you my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.19,1:07:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活下去的\N{\rEng}You shall be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.55,1:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的命换你的 珠迪丝\N{\rEng}I give you my life, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.68,1:07:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢\N{\rEng}I'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.33,1:07:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个男子汉 爹\N{\rEng}I'll be brave, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.81,1:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢\N{\rEng}I'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.30,1:07:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢\N{\rEng}I'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.74,1:07:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个男子汉 爹\N{\rEng}I'll be brave, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.49,1:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个男子汉\N{\rEng}I'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.66,1:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我很勇敢\N{\rEng}I'll be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.63,1:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,驭\N{\rEng}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.76,1:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快\N{\rEng}Quick as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.16,1:09:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特\N{\rEng}Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.83,1:09:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒 你不该在这儿睡\N{\rEng}Hamnet, you're not supposed to be down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.20,1:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,来 我抱你上楼睡觉去...\N{\rEng}I need to take you up to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.13,1:09:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特\N{\rEng}Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.29,1:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥？\N{\rEng}Hamnet?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.91,1:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\N{\rEng}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.69,1:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,娘\N{\rEng}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.38,1:10:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,娘啊\N{\rEng}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.69,1:10:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特\N{\rEng}Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.68,1:11:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你得张开嘴\N{\rEng}You must open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.83,1:11:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,会没事的\N{\rEng}All will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.85,1:11:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他在发烧\N{\rEng}He's burning.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.59,1:11:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,烧得太高了\N{\rEng}He's burning up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.01,1:11:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,药不起作用 不起作用\N{\rEng}It will not sti-- It will not stick!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.20,1:11:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拿石头 拿石头\N{\rEng}A stone. There's a stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.20,1:11:26.35,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【有洞的石头: 当时民间信仰认为病气能从一孔进 一孔出】
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.51,1:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,楼上有块中间有洞的石头\N{\rEng}There's a stone upstairs with a hole in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.32,1:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在他床边 快去拿来 快去\N{\rEng}By his bedside. Bring it down. I need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.35,1:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还要盐 拿盐 得撒盐\N{\rEng}And, um, uh, salt. Get salt.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.35,1:11:32.69,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【撒盐: 当时认为能建立保护屏障 驱挡邪灵和病气】
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.51,1:11:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能去拿吗？\N{\rEng}Get it. Can you give it?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.80,1:11:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,多拿点盐 有多少拿多少\N{\rEng}Can you f-fetch me some salt, as much salt as you have.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.69,1:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,水 还要水\N{\rEng}Water. We need water.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.37,1:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他 他烧得太厉害了\N{\rEng}He's... he's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.31,1:11:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太厉害了\N{\rEng}He's burning.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.84,1:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子 娘在这儿\N{\rEng}My love. Mama's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.90,1:11:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 都会好的\N{\rEng}All will be well. All will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.85,1:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都会好的\N{\rEng}All will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.86,1:11:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,都会好的\N{\rEng}All will be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.23,1:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 别怕\N{\rEng}Hamnet, don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.54,1:11:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的\N{\rEng}No need to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.15,1:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都会没事的 娘在这儿\N{\rEng}All will be well. Mommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.13,1:12:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在 没事的\N{\rEng}Mommy's here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.81,1:12:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,娘在这儿\N{\rEng}Mommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.22,1:12:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 娘在这儿\N{\rEng}Look at me. Mommy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.01,1:12:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不 绝不会放手的\N{\rEng}I will never, ever let you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.30,1:12:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\N{\rEng}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.19,1:12:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,娘绝不 绝不会放手的\N{\rEng}I will never, ever let you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.99,1:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,娘的心肝啊\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.51,1:12:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,心肝啊\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.40,1:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱莎 把珠迪丝抱到厨房去\N{\rEng}Eliza, take Judith to the kitchen and keep her there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.61,1:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不走\N{\rEng}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.94,1:12:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我得陪他 - 带她走\N{\rEng}- He needs me! - Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.24,1:12:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我要陪我哥\N{\rEng}He needs me!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.63,1:12:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不走\N{\rEng}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.37,1:12:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,缬草啊...\N{\rEng}Valerian...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.60,1:12:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 哈姆奈特 哈姆奈特\N{\rEng}Hamnet. Hamnet. Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.39,1:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 坚持住 求你了\N{\rEng}Hamnet, you have to stay. Hamnet, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.29,1:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 求你了 你要坚持住 别离开我们\N{\rEng}Hamnet, please. You have to stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.30,1:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,娘需要你 我们都需要你\N{\rEng}Mama needs you. We need you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.90,1:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 住手 够了 - 别离开我们 坚持住 坚持\N{\rEng}- Stop! Enough! - Stay with us. Stay, stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.10,1:13:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了 哈姆奈特 坚持住 坚持住\N{\rEng}Please, Hamnet. Hamnet, Hamnet, Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.53,1:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别折腾他了 - 求求你了 哈姆奈特\N{\rEng}- Let him alone! - Hamnet, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.89,1:13:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不出来吗 太晚了\N{\rEng}Can't you see that it's too late for him!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.04,1:13:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 求你了\N{\rEng}Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.39,1:13:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特？\N{\rEng}Hamnet?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.82,1:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特 哈姆奈特 求你了 哈姆奈特\N{\rEng}Hamnet. Hamnet. Please. Hamnet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.35,1:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子没了\N{\rEng}My son is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.77,1:14:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没了 我的儿子\N{\rEng}Just so bereft... it's my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.43,1:14:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没了 我...\N{\rEng}I've lost my...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.82,1:15:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我看灯还亮着 我也睡不着\N{\rEng}I saw the light, and I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.49,1:15:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\rEng}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.14,1:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 孩子 不行\N{\rEng}Oh, child, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.72,1:15:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 快去睡觉 - 没事 没事 让她看吧\N{\rEng}- No, no, no. Go to bed. - No, no, let-let her stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.08,1:15:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是我害的 娘 都是我害的\N{\rEng}It is my fault, Mama. It is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.28,1:15:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\rEng}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.20,1:16:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝 这不是你的错\N{\rEng}It is not your fault, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.16,1:16:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他替了我\N{\rEng}But he changed places with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.35,1:16:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他骗了它\N{\rEng}He tricked it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.75,1:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他骗了什么？\N{\rEng}He tricked what?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.21,1:16:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,死神\N{\rEng}Death.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.83,1:16:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,珠迪丝\N{\rEng}Judith.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.94,1:16:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它来找我时 却把他夺走了\N{\rEng}It took him when it came for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.44,1:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这话绝对不许再说\N{\rEng}Never say those words to anyone ever again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.93,1:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥是因为发烧走的\N{\rEng}The fever came for your brother, and it took him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.88,1:16:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看看他吗？\N{\rEng}Do you wish to see him?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.38,1:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.39,1:16:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 去看看他\N{\rEng}Go on. You can see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.27,1:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的是他吗？\N{\rEng}Is it really him?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.77,1:16:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.79,1:16:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这 这不像我哥\N{\rEng}It-it doesn't look like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.59,1:17:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.59,1:17:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是他\N{\rEng}It's not him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.25,1:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rEng}It's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.06,1:17:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我哥\N{\rEng}It's not him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.78,1:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,天 天还没亮呢\N{\rEng}It-It's-it's not morning yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.51,1:17:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还没给他收拾好呢\N{\rEng}We haven't prepared him properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.19,1:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我来晚了吗？\N{\rEng}Am I too late?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.30,1:17:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是你 - 爹\N{\rEng}- It's you. - Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.45,1:17:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是你\N{\rEng}It's you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.70,1:17:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是我\N{\rEng}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.01,1:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子呢？\N{\rEng}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.52,1:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪儿...\N{\rEng}Where is...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.53,1:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他在...\N{\rEng}Where...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.84,1:19:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是我儿子\N{\rEng}It's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.43,1:19:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的儿子啊\N{\rEng}It's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.18,1:19:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我没预见到\N{\rEng}I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.19,1:19:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我该多留心哈姆奈特的\N{\rEng}I should've paid him more attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.52,1:19:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为会失去珠迪丝\N{\rEng}I always thought she was the one to be taken away
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.64,1:19:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到是儿子\N{\rEng}when all the while it was him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.06,1:19:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我太蠢了\N{\rEng}I'm a fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.07,1:19:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 没人能救他\N{\rEng}No, there's nothing anyone could have done to save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.96,1:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经尽力了\N{\rEng}You did everything that you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.70,1:19:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是尽力了\N{\rEng}Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.17,1:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可你人呢？\N{\rEng}You weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.81,1:19:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿把心掏给他\N{\rEng}I would have cut my heart out and given it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.60,1:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的命换他的命\N{\rEng}I would have laid my life down on the ground for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.45,1:20:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我懂 我懂 - 可上天不收\N{\rEng}- I-I know. I know. - And no one would take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.36,1:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可你... - 不 你不懂\N{\rEng}- But you... - No, you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.13,1:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么可能懂 你都不在啊\N{\rEng}You don't know. You weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.56,1:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他在折磨中死去\N{\rEng}He died in agony.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.22,1:20:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\rEng}I...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.59,1:20:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 受尽了折磨 - 安妮丝\N{\rEng}- He was in agony. - Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.53,1:20:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他哭个不停 他哭啊 哭啊\N{\rEng}He cried and he cried
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.07,1:20:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-  哭啊 哭啊 哭啊 - 安妮丝 别这样\N{\rEng}- and he cried and he cried. - Agnes, stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.75,1:20:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他小小的身子在剧痛中抽搐 - 嘘\N{\rEng}- And his little body was wracked in pain. - Shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.34,1:20:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别让我闭嘴\N{\rEng}No, don't shush me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.60,1:20:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时好害怕\N{\rEng}He was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.00,1:20:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你却没在身边 - 我知道\N{\rEng}- And you weren't here. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.99,1:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么办法都用了\N{\rEng}I tried everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.82,1:20:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你做了\N{\rEng}I know you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.55,1:20:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我什么都试过了 - 你已经尽了一切\N{\rEng}- I tried everything I could. - You did everything that you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.26,1:20:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经用尽了一切办法\N{\rEng}You did everything that you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.00,1:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一切办法\N{\rEng}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.12,1:20:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一切办法\N{\rEng}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.60,1:20:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝 安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes. Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.48,1:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我会捎信的 安妮丝\N{\rEng}I will send word, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.46,1:21:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,捎信？\N{\rEng}You'll send word?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.02,1:21:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 捎给谁啊？ - 给你啊\N{\rEng}- To whom? - To you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.86,1:21:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿啊\N{\rEng}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.98,1:21:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说到了伦敦我会给你捎信的\N{\rEng}What I meant was that I shall send word when I reach London.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.55,1:21:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦？\N{\rEng}London?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.71,1:21:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\rEng}I must leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.81,1:21:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,走？你怎么能走？\N{\rEng}Leave? How can you leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.60,1:21:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,世界不会因为我们就停下来 安妮丝\N{\rEng}The world does simply not stand still, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.02,1:21:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦还有人在等我\N{\rEng}There are people waiting for me in London.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.41,1:21:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,演出季马上就要开始了\N{\rEng}The season is about to begin,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.77,1:21:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的剧团随时都会从肯特郡回来\N{\rEng}and my company shall return from Kent any day now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.56,1:22:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就得走了\N{\rEng}I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.12,1:22:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在？\N{\rEng}Now?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.31,1:22:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有个商队要出发\N{\rEng}There's a traveling party leaving today,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.01,1:22:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有匹多余的马 现在就得走\N{\rEng}and they have a spare horse, so yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.64,1:22:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,照看好女儿们 我回来时会...\N{\rEng}Look after the girls, and I will return to--
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.64,1:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\rEng}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.77,1:22:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我\N{\rEng}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.54,1:22:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 你走吧\N{\rEng}Go. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.34,1:23:10.30,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(995,655)\frz7.1\fax-0.15\an8\fnSource Han Serif SC\b1\c&H0F0F0F&\fs90}哈姆奈特
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.84,1:23:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,“蒙晨暮鼓催岁长”\N{\rEng}"When I do count the clock that tells the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.51,1:23:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“夕太沉沉入幽光”\N{\rEng}"And see the brave day sunk in hideous night;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.39,1:23:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,“芳草奇花香自散”\N{\rEng}"When I behold the violet past prime,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.87,1:23:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,“青丝墨字今已霜”\N{\rEng}"And sable curls all silver'd o'er with white;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.94,1:23:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,“繁荫不复幕沧桑”\N{\rEng}"When lofty trees I see barren of leaves
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.03,1:23:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“牧群归舍众组忙”\N{\rEng}"Which erst from the heat did canopy the herd,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.84,1:23:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,“夏末青禾束成囊”\N{\rEng}"And summer's green all girded up in sheaves
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.97,1:23:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,“犹似亡魂缠白裳”\N{\rEng}"Borne on the bier with white and bristly beard;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.86,1:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“容颜岂非浮云妆”\N{\rEng}"Then of thy beauty do I question make,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.36,1:23:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,“终将消散入苍茫”\N{\rEng}"Thou among the wastes of time must go,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.34,1:23:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,“芬芳娇艳随风扬”\N{\rEng}"Since sweets and beauties do themselves forsake
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.15,1:23:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,“新生如笋催人苍”\N{\rEng}"And die as fast as they see others grow;
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.43,1:23:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“时光镰刀谁能挡”\N{\rEng}"And nothing gainst time's scythe can make defense
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.54,1:23:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,“勇敢生育续春阳”\N{\rEng}Save breed, to brave him when he takes thee hence."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.54,1:23:56.97,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【十四行诗: 现代编号第12首 以时间流逝与生育为主题】
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.97,1:23:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,能再读一遍吗？\N{\rEng}Will you read it again?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.32,1:24:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不了\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.95,1:24:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经读了三遍了\N{\rEng}I've read it three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.01,1:24:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,行了\N{\rEng}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.01,1:24:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱们开始拆礼物吧 - 什么礼物？伦敦的吗？\N{\rEng}- Shall we do presents? - Presents? from London?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.62,1:24:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,给你的梳子 小珠\N{\rEng}A hair comb for you, Jude.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.84,1:24:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爱惜点用 别弄坏了\N{\rEng}Mind you, you'll have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.28,1:24:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是给你的 安妮丝\N{\rEng}This is for you, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.36,1:24:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 红宝石吗？ - 是的\N{\rEng}- A ruby, is it? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.03,1:24:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,从没见过这么漂亮的\N{\rEng}It's the finest I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.28,1:24:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在议论那栋新房子\N{\rEng}Everyone's talking about the new house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.83,1:24:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是斯特拉特福镇上最大的房子\N{\rEng}It's the biggest in Stratford.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.68,1:24:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,房间多到人进去都能走丢\N{\rEng}There are so many rooms. One could get lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.57,1:24:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜 那就好好照看好\N{\rEng}You shall keep the keys, Susanna.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.95,1:24:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,打理好咱们的房子\N{\rEng}You shall manage the house well.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.86,1:24:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,娘 你戴上试试\N{\rEng}Put it on, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.41,1:25:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥巴塞洛缪带你看过那栋房子了吗？\N{\rEng}Did Bartholomew show you the new house?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.71,1:25:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看了\N{\rEng}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.27,1:25:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗？\N{\rEng}Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.53,1:25:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不亲自带我去看的？\N{\rEng}Why didn't you show me yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.38,1:25:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是怕我不愿离开吗？\N{\rEng}Were you afraid I wouldn't leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.65,1:25:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为哈姆奈特死在这个房子里\N{\rEng}'Cause Hamnet died here in this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.13,1:25:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想他在哪儿？\N{\rEng}You know, I'm constantly wondering where he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.38,1:25:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他去了哪儿？\N{\rEng}Or where he has gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.02,1:25:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我做什么 脑子里都是他在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Whatever I'm doing, I'm wondering, "Where is he?"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.73,1:26:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能就这么凭空没了啊\N{\rEng}I mean, he can't have just vanished.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.76,1:26:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要找到他\N{\rEng}All he needs is for me to find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.78,1:26:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定在哪个地方\N{\rEng}He must be somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.36,1:26:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都一年了还是这样 我真害怕自己会疯掉\N{\rEng}I fear I may run mad with it, even now, a year on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.35,1:26:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一年算什么啊\N{\rEng}A year is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.46,1:26:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一年什么都不是 每时每刻...\N{\rEng}A year is nothing. It's every second...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.42,1:26:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,每分每秒 每天每年\N{\rEng}every minute, every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.04,1:26:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么可能停止寻找啊\N{\rEng}We may never stop looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.77,1:26:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 安妮丝\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.80,1:26:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗？我说对不起 安妮丝\N{\rEng}Did you hear me? I said that I'm sorry, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.21,1:26:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么道歉？ - 为这一切\N{\rEng}- For what? - For everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.50,1:26:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你被那地方缠住了 - 为...\N{\rEng}- You're caught by that place. - For...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.02,1:26:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么地方？ - 你脑子里那个地方\N{\rEng}- What place? - That place in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.95,1:26:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说 那地方比什么都好\N{\rEng}It is now more real to you than anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.62,1:26:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,连咱儿子死了都留不住你\N{\rEng}Not even the death of our child can keep you from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.97,1:26:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆奈特死了\N{\rEng}Hamnet died.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.29,1:26:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,死得很惨\N{\rEng}A horrible death.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.46,1:26:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你本该在场\N{\rEng}And you should have been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.78,1:27:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可跟他道个别\N{\rEng}You could have bid him farewell.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.67,1:27:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了什么？\N{\rEng}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.05,1:27:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\rEng}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.95,1:27:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.22,1:27:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有？\N{\rEng}Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.98,1:27:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\rEng}Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.95,1:27:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.38,1:28:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是回伦敦吧\N{\rEng}You should go back to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.74,1:28:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不用为我们操心\N{\rEng}You need not concern yourself with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.37,1:28:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你我们的日子也照过\N{\rEng}Get along just fine without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.19,1:28:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“这句话从前是个似是而非的悖论”\N{\rEng}This was sometime a paradox,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.38,1:28:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,“如今已被时间所证实”\N{\rEng}but now the time gives it proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.67,1:28:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,“我确实曾爱过你”\N{\rEng}I did love you once.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.50,1:28:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,“没错 殿下 您确实让我信以为真”\N{\rEng}Indeed, my lord, you made me believe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.34,1:28:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“你当初就不该相信我”\N{\rEng}You should not have believed me,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.69,1:28:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,“美德嫁接到我们这罪恶的老树干上 也...”\N{\rEng}for virtue cannot so inoculate our old stock for...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.15,1:28:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,“你当初就不该相信我”\N{\rEng}You should not have believed me,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.04,1:28:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,“美德嫁接到我们这罪恶的老树干上”\N{\rEng}for virtue cannot so inoculate our old stock
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.89,1:28:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,“也结不出好果”\N{\rEng}but we shall relish of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.77,1:28:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“我从未真爱过你”\N{\rEng}I loved you not.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.66,1:28:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,“那我真是被深深欺骗了”\N{\rEng}I was the more deceived.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.38,1:28:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,“去美人庵吧”\N{\rEng}Get thee to a nunnery.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.38,1:28:57.22,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【美人庵: 指女性宗教修行场所 又为妓院俚语 此处含贬低之意】
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.99,1:28:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“干嘛非得生出一堆罪人来？”\N{\rEng}Why wouldst thou be a breeder of sinners?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.22,1:28:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己还算个老实人”\N{\rEng}I am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.65,1:29:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过却多得数不清”\N{\rEng}but yet I could accuse me of such things
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.79,1:29:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,“最大的莫过于...”\N{\rEng}that it were better to...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.79,1:29:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,重来\N{\rEng}Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.36,1:29:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“去美人庵吧”\N{\rEng}Get thee to a nunnery.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.45,1:29:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,“干嘛非得生出一堆罪人来？”\N{\rEng}Why wouldst thou be a breeder of sinners?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.31,1:29:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己也算个老实人 但...”\N{\rEng}I am myself indifferent honest, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.73,1:29:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,重来 是“我自己还算个老实人” 重来\N{\rEng}Again. "I am myself indifferent honest." Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.77,1:29:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己还算个老实人”\N{\rEng}I am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.80,1:29:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过却多得数不清 最大的莫过于”\N{\rEng}but yet I could accuse me of such things that it were better
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.26,1:29:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- “我娘把我生了出来” - 重来\N{\rEng}- my mother had not borne me. - Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.98,1:29:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“我这个人...”\N{\rEng}I, myself...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.63,1:29:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃... - 再来\N{\rEng}- And... - Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.53,1:29:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“我这个人...自己还算个...”\N{\rEng}I, myself, am indifferent...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.21,1:29:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是“我自己”\N{\rEng}"I am myself."
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.85,1:29:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己还算个老实人”\N{\rEng}I am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.93,1:29:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过却多得数不清...”\N{\rEng}but yet I could accuse me of such things that it were...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.10,1:29:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\rEng}Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.43,1:29:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过却多得数不清...”\N{\rEng}But yet I could accuse me of such things that it were...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.05,1:29:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,重来\N{\rEng}Again!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.47,1:29:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,“我自己还算个老实人”\N{\rEng}I am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.07,1:29:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我的罪过...”\N{\rEng}but yet I could accuse me of such...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.06,1:29:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本没投入\N{\rEng}You are simply mouthing the words!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.51,1:29:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己还算个老实人\N{\rEng}I am myself indifferent honest,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.78,1:29:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的罪过却多得数不清\N{\rEng}but yet I could accuse me of such things
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.07,1:30:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,最大的莫过于我娘把我生了出来\N{\rEng}that it were better my mother had not borne me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.65,1:30:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我这人自傲 报复心强 野心大\N{\rEng}I am very proud, revengeful, ambitious,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.82,1:30:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子里装的那些坏主意\N{\rEng}with more offenses at my beck
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.52,1:30:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,多到我都数不清\N{\rEng}than I have thoughts to put them in,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.23,1:30:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,想都想不尽 干也干不完\N{\rEng}imagination to give them shape or time to act them in.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.33,1:30:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这样的人\N{\rEng}Now, what should such fellows as I do
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.02,1:30:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在天地之间苟活 有什么用？\N{\rEng}crawling between heaven and earth?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.85,1:30:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们全是烂透的坏人\N{\rEng}We are arrant knaves all.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.24,1:30:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你可千万不要信我们\N{\rEng}Believe none of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.96,1:30:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的美人庵吧 重来\N{\rEng}Go thy ways to a nunnery. Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.67,1:31:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,生存...\N{\rEng}To be...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.26,1:31:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还是毁灭...\N{\rEng}...or not to be...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.91,1:31:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个问题\N{\rEng}...that is the question:
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.58,1:31:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种更高贵？是默然 忍受...\N{\rEng}Whether 'tis nobler in the mind to... suffer
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.30,1:31:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,命运投来的巨石...\N{\rEng}The slings and arrows of...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.73,1:31:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,射来的毒箭？\N{\rEng}...outrageous fortune...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.25,1:31:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还是...\N{\rEng}...Or...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.04,1:31:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,挺身反抗...\N{\rEng}...to take arms against a...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.76,1:32:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,汹涌的苦海...\N{\rEng}...sea of troubles,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.10,1:32:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,通过斗争...\N{\rEng}And by opposing...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.30,1:32:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,渡向彼岸？\N{\rEng}...end them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.95,1:33:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我祈求那些树啊 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ I pray that those trees ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.17,1:33:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 还我男孩来 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Will return my boy ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.34,1:33:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 只因... ♪\N{\rEng}♪ For ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.59,1:33:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 那只温柔的知更鸟 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Sweet bonny Robin ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.85,1:33:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 是我仅有的幸福 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Is all my joy. ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.85,1:33:28.76,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【《我那去了绿林的知更鸟》: 英国民谣 绿林象征身后世界 知更鸟象征逝者】
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.28,1:33:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝？\N{\rEng}Agnes?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.68,1:33:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我碰巧来镇上\N{\rEng}I... I was in town, and I...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.77,1:33:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就想顺路来看下你\N{\rEng}I thought I would pay you a visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.38,1:33:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你公公约翰去世了 替你们难过\N{\rEng}I was very sorry to hear about John's passing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.46,1:33:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫还好吧\N{\rEng}How's your husband?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.23,1:33:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,失去父亲 真是件悲痛的事啊\N{\rEng}It's a... it's a terrible thing to lose one's father.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.24,1:33:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他好得很\N{\rEng}He's well.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.83,1:33:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,忙得要命 还在搞一出喜剧\N{\rEng}He's very busy. He's preparing a comedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.58,1:33:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他的新剧可不是喜剧\N{\rEng}His new play is not a comedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.35,1:34:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是悲剧\N{\rEng}It's a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.52,1:34:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该早知道了\N{\rEng}But you knew that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.02,1:34:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,镇上人人都在谈论\N{\rEng}Everyone in town is talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.88,1:34:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是劝过你别嫁给他...\N{\rEng}I did warn you about marrying him...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.13,1:34:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别装作疼我\N{\rEng}Don't pretend that you care for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.23,1:34:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是我娘 永远也不是\N{\rEng}You are not my mother, and you never were.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.94,1:34:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 安妮丝\N{\rEng}Good day, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.00,1:34:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他都好几个月没跟我们联系了\N{\rEng}He's not spoken to us for months.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.41,1:34:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么能\N{\rEng}How could he...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.79,1:34:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么能不告诉我们呢？\N{\rEng}How could he not tell us?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.65,1:34:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想看看吗？\N{\rEng}Do you not wonder what is in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.43,1:34:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看什么？\N{\rEng}In what?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.31,1:34:56.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\frz-33.0\fax-0.05\an8\fnSource Han Serif SC\b1\c&H0F0F0F&\fs90\move(1164,733,1101,620,1460,2300)}《哈姆雷特的悲剧》
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.71,1:34:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这剧\N{\rEng}The play.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.10,1:36:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们找谁呢？\N{\rEng}Who are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.48,1:36:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉·莎士比亚\N{\rEng}William Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.98,1:36:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是他的家人 从斯特拉特福来的\N{\rEng}We're his family from Stratford.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.86,1:36:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,上楼 他住阁楼\N{\rEng}Go up the stairs. He lives in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.14,1:36:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有斯特拉特福最大房子的人\N{\rEng}Why would the man with the largest house in Stratford
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.46,1:36:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会住在这样的地方？\N{\rEng}be living here?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.97,1:36:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\rEng}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.37,1:36:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为...\N{\rEng}I thought...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.34,1:36:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为他...\N{\rEng}I thought he...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.70,1:37:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办？\N{\rEng}What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.79,1:37:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,敞开心扉\N{\rEng}Keep your heart open.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.60,1:37:24.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(944,326)\frx48.0\frz0.5\fay0.04\an8\b1\fs70\1c&H6F7480&\3c&&H2F2D66&\bord6\shad0\alpha&HFF&\t(0,550,\alpha&H00&)}天下皆为舞{\alpha&HFF&\t(500,2700,{\alpha&H00&}台
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.60,1:37:24.66,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【拉丁格言"天下皆为舞台 人人都是演员" 莎士比亚《皆大欢喜》亦用此意象】
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.66,1:37:32.33,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(965,512)\an8\b1\fs12\1c&H4B525C\3c&&H2F2D66&\bord0.1\shad0\fscx95\fscy95\t(0,7666,\fscx100\fscy100)}天下皆为舞台
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.33,1:37:36.30,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\move(974,274,974,244,0,3959)\frx-50.0\an8\b1\fs60\1c&H4B525C\3c&&H2F2D66&\bord1\shad0\fscx95\fscy95\t(0,1,\fscx100\fscy100)}天下皆为舞台
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.59,1:38:02.78,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 当时剧场分为站票 看台 包厢等级】
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.80,1:38:46.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（《哈姆奈特的悲剧》）
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.10,1:39:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁呀？ - 不 先回答我\N{\rEng}- Who's there? - Nay, answer me:
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.76,1:39:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,出来 报上名来\N{\rEng}stand and unfold yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.88,1:39:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,国王万岁\N{\rEng}Long live the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.88,1:39:15.42,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【国王万岁: 执勤人员碰头暗号】
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.43,1:39:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,伯纳多？\N{\rEng}Bernardo?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.42,1:39:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要是碰到我的夜班同伴\N{\rEng}If you do meet Horatio and Marcellus,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.60,1:39:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,霍拉旭和马塞拉斯 叫他们速来\N{\rEng}The rivals to my watch, bid them make haste.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.88,1:39:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们好像来了 站住 谁\N{\rEng}I think I hear them. Stand, ho!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.75,1:39:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁？\N{\rEng}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.66,1:39:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,它今晚又现身了吗？\N{\rEng}Has this thing appeared again tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.89,1:39:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还没看见 - 霍拉旭说...\N{\rEng}- I have seen nothing. - Horatio says...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.72,1:39:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这演的什么啊\N{\rEng}What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.72,1:39:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这不过是我们的幻觉\N{\rEng}...'tis but our fantasy...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.45,1:39:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾和他说过 他就是不信...\N{\rEng}...and will not let belief take hold of him touching...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.95,1:39:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这和我儿子有什么关系？\N{\rEng}What has any of this to do with my son?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.95,1:39:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们已经见过两次这可怕的景象...\N{\rEng}...this dreaded sight twice seen of us...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.99,1:39:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很害怕\N{\rEng}These men are frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.65,1:39:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么好怕的\N{\rEng}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.54,1:39:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}别不信 让我们再给你解释一遍...\N{\rEng}And let us once again assail your ears...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.92,1:39:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在提防一个幽灵\N{\rEng}They watch for a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.07,1:39:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天这个时候 北极星西侧的星到这个位置时...\N{\rEng}...when yond same star that's westward from the pole...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.78,1:39:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,幽灵？\N{\rEng}Ghost?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.92,1:39:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,钟刚好敲了一下...\N{\rEng}...The bell then beating one...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.14,1:39:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快住嘴 别说了\N{\rEng}Peace; break thee off!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.33,1:39:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看 它又现身了\N{\rEng}Look where it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.95,1:39:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一模一样 就像那位已故的先王\N{\rEng}In the same figure, like the king that's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.72,1:40:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看 它阔步离去了\N{\rEng}See, it stalks away!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.42,1:40:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他\N{\rEng}That was him.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.44,1:40:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能告诉我 为什么...\N{\rEng}...Tell me why this same...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.57,1:40:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是威廉 - 嘘\N{\rEng}- That was Will. - Shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.25,1:40:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不是演员 - 不 不\N{\rEng}- He's not in the play. - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.70,1:40:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那幽灵就是威廉演的\N{\rEng}It was Will as a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.00,1:40:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才向我们显灵的那位先王\N{\rEng}Our last king, Whose image but now appeared to us,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.25,1:40:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,正是那场决斗中 英勇的哈姆雷特国王...\N{\rEng}Was dared to the combat; our valiant Hamlet...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.22,1:40:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆雷特\N{\rEng}Hamlet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.55,1:40:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了 你听到了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you hear... did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.57,1:40:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.52,1:40:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们念了 念了他的名字\N{\rEng}They said his-- they said his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.45,1:40:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮丝\N{\rEng}Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.88,1:40:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安妮丝 别 - 让开\N{\rEng}- Agnes, wait. - Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.22,1:40:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,安静\N{\rEng}Please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.97,1:40:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们干嘛念他的名字啊\N{\rEng}Wait, did they say his name? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.45,1:40:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,别自找苦吃\N{\rEng}Do not upset yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.62,1:40:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他凭什么 凭什么喊我儿子的名字？\N{\rEng}Why is-- Why did he use his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.45,1:40:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他当他谁啊 - 安静\N{\rEng}- I don't know him. - Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.08,1:40:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...依我之见\N{\rEng}...and by my advice,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.26,1:40:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不如将我们今晚所见\N{\rEng}Let us impart what we have seen tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.92,1:40:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,禀告给年轻的王子...\N{\rEng}Unto the young prince...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.14,1:40:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不许念我儿子的名字\N{\rEng}Don't you dare pronounce my son's name!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.69,1:40:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\rEng}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.87,1:40:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...对我们沉默的幽灵 会对他说话\N{\rEng}...dumb to us, will speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.43,1:41:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说大家对我亲爱的王兄死讯\N{\rEng}Though yet of our dear brother's death,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.98,1:41:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还记忆犹新\N{\rEng}The memory be green,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.43,1:41:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们要节哀顺变\N{\rEng}Yet so far hath discretion fought with nature
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.79,1:41:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在深切缅怀他的同时\N{\rEng}That we with wisest sorrow think on him,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.04,1:41:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也要为我们自身着想啊\N{\rEng}Together with remembrance of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.99,1:41:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了 我不能再看下去了\N{\rEng}I will not stay a minute longer to be a part of this jest.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.05,1:41:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别急 再看一会儿 - 我的侄儿\N{\rEng}- Wait. One moment. - ...my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.70,1:41:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我要回家 - 哈姆雷特\N{\rEng}- No. I want to go home. -  Hamlet...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.70,1:41:20.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【哈姆雷特: 原著中先王与王子同名皆为哈姆雷特】
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.02,1:41:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也是我的儿子\N{\rEng}and my son...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.58,1:41:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么还一脸愁云？\N{\rEng}How is it that the clouds still hang on you?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.94,1:41:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的好哈姆雷特 脱去这沉重的黑衣\N{\rEng}Good Hamlet, cast thy nighted color off.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.21,1:41:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别总是低眉垂眼的\N{\rEng}Do not for ever with thy vailed lids
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.83,1:41:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛要从尘土中寻出你高贵的父亲\N{\rEng}Seek for thy noble father in the dust.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.17,1:41:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,万物有生必有死\N{\rEng}All that lives must die,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.11,1:41:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,顺其自然 谁都会踏入永恒\N{\rEng}Passing through nature to eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.32,1:41:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 母后 这确实是常理\N{\rEng}Ay, madam, it is common.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.94,1:41:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但我心中的郁结\N{\rEng}But I have that within which passes show.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.85,1:41:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,远非这些丧服哀装所能表达\N{\rEng}These are but the trappings and the suits of woe.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.96,1:41:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,固执地沉溺于哀伤\N{\rEng}To persevere In obstinate condolement
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.68,1:41:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种逆天的愚行\N{\rEng}is a course of impious stubbornness.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.09,1:42:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是堂堂男子的悲伤\N{\rEng}'Tis unmanly grief.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.77,1:42:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是对天意的违抗\N{\rEng}It shows a will most incorrect to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.95,1:42:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.70,1:42:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真想这 这沉重的肉体消融\N{\rEng}This too, too solid flesh would melt,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.94,1:42:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,化为晨露消散\N{\rEng}Thaw and resolve itself into a dew.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.91,1:42:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真想永恒的真神\N{\rEng}Or that the Everlasting had not fixed
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.91,1:42:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,未曾禁止自杀这罪孽\N{\rEng}His canon gainst self-slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.97,1:42:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是一座荒芜不治 杂草丛生\N{\rEng}'Tis an unweeded garden That grows to seed;
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.90,1:42:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,长满毒花恶草的花园\N{\rEng}things rank and gross in nature possess it merely.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.70,1:42:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谁曾料到啊\N{\rEng}That it should come to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.19,1:43:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,才死了两个月\N{\rEng}But two months dead--
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.43,1:43:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不 还没满两个月\N{\rEng}nay, not so much, not two--
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.04,1:43:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一位多么杰出的国王 如同太阳神\N{\rEng}So excellent a king, that was to this
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.04,1:43:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在这位 却像只肮脏的禽兽\N{\rEng}Hyperion to a... a satyr.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.27,1:43:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你要领我上哪儿去？\N{\rEng}Whither wilt thou lead me?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.29,1:43:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快说 我不跟你走\N{\rEng}Speak. I'll go no further.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.02,1:43:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你父亲的灵魂\N{\rEng}I am thy father's spirit,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.57,1:43:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被判在夜间游走于这大地\N{\rEng}Doomed for a certain term to walk the night,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.19,1:43:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,白天则要忍受地狱烈火的焚烧\N{\rEng}And for the day confined to fast in fires.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.87,1:43:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的时辰快到了\N{\rEng}My hour is almost come
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.64,1:43:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我又得回到硫磺的火焰中...\N{\rEng}When I to sulfurous and tormenting flames
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.48,1:43:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,去遭受痛苦的煎熬\N{\rEng}Must render up myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.02,1:43:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 唉 可怜的幽灵 - 不 不要可怜我...\N{\rEng}- Alas, poor ghost. - No, pity me not...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.45,1:43:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要留心听着我要告诉你的话\N{\rEng}...but lend thy serious hearing to what I shall unfold.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.56,1:43:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,听好\N{\rEng}List.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.34,1:43:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,听好 啊 听好了\N{\rEng}List, oh, list.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.74,1:43:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你曾深爱过你的父亲\N{\rEng}If thou didst ever thy father love...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.30,1:43:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.10,1:43:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,且慢 我仿佛闻到了清晨的气息\N{\rEng}But soft, methinks I scent the morning air.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.15,1:43:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我长话短说 那天我照常在花园里午睡\N{\rEng}Brief let me be. Sleeping within my orchard.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.91,1:44:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你叔父趁我熟睡之际偷溜进来\N{\rEng}Upon my secure hour, thy uncle stole
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.32,1:44:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着一瓶天杀的剧毒毒液\N{\rEng}With juice of cursed hebona in a vile,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.49,1:44:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,灌入了我的耳朵\N{\rEng}Within the porches of my ears did pour
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.26,1:44:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这麻风病般的毒液...\N{\rEng}The leprous distillment...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.50,1:44:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,毒性之大 嗜血如仇\N{\rEng}...whose effect Holds such an enmity with blood of man
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.37,1:44:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它顺着血管流动得比水银还快\N{\rEng}That swift as quicksilver it courses through
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.17,1:44:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,流遍全身七窍八脉\N{\rEng}The natural gates and alleys of the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.13,1:44:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,突然一下子\N{\rEng}And with a sudden vigor it doth posset
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.28,1:44:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就凝固了我的血...\N{\rEng}And curd, like...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.25,1:44:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,像卤水点豆腐一样\N{\rEng}...eager droppings into milk,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.99,1:44:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,把我健康的血液彻底摧毁了\N{\rEng}The thin and wholesome blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.14,1:44:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我就这样被毒害了\N{\rEng}So did it mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.54,1:44:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,转眼间我全身长满了烂疮...\N{\rEng}A most instant tetter barked about...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.17,1:44:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如癞病般浑身长满可憎的痂皮\N{\rEng}...Most lazar-like, with vile and loathsome crust,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.20,1:44:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,体无完肤\N{\rEng}All my smooth body.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.44,1:44:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.53,1:44:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,惨呀\N{\rEng}Horrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.31,1:45:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 惨啊 太惨了\N{\rEng}Oh, horrible. Most horrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.84,1:45:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你还有人性 就不要再忍了...\N{\rEng}If thou hast nature in thee, bear it not...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.22,1:45:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他成了我们的儿子\N{\rEng}He has swapped places with our son.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.67,1:45:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\N{\rEng}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.99,1:45:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,回头看我\N{\rEng}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.21,1:46:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,萤 萤火虫的微光已经暗淡\N{\rEng}The... the glowworm shows the matin to be near,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.91,1:46:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明就要来了\N{\rEng}And 'gins to pale his uneffectual fires.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.13,1:46:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子啊\N{\rEng}My boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.41,1:46:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再会了\N{\rEng}Adieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.13,1:46:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,再会了\N{\rEng}Adieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.48,1:46:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再会了\N{\rEng}Adieu.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.76,1:47:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,记着我\N{\rEng}Remember me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.54,1:48:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,生存还是毁灭\N{\rEng}To be, or not to be,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.70,1:48:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个问题\N{\rEng}that is the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.51,1:48:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种更高贵？是默然忍受\N{\rEng}Whether 'tis nobler in the mind to suffer
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.65,1:48:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,命运投来的巨石 射来的毒箭？\N{\rEng}The slings and arrows of outrageous fortune,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.62,1:48:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还是挺身反抗汹涌的苦海\N{\rEng}Or to take arms against a sea of troubles
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.08,1:48:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,通过斗争 渡向彼岸？\N{\rEng}And, by opposing, end them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.53,1:48:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,死了 沉睡了\N{\rEng}To die, to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.25,1:48:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就那样了\N{\rEng}No more.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.70,1:48:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要是一场睡眠可以终结\N{\rEng}And by a sleep, to say we end
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.95,1:48:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这些血肉之躯生来要承受的\N{\rEng}The heartache and the thousand natural shocks
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.36,1:48:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,万千苦难 那可是天大的好事\N{\rEng}That flesh is heir to-- 'tis a consummation
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.81,1:48:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是求之不得的结局\N{\rEng}Devoutly to be wished.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.34,1:48:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,死了\N{\rEng}To die,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.62,1:48:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沉睡了 没准还有梦呢\N{\rEng}To sleep, perchance to dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.46,1:48:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这就是问题\N{\rEng}Ay, there's the rub.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.74,1:48:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,摆脱了这凡尘肉体 在那死亡的沉睡中\N{\rEng}For in that sleep of death, what dreams may come
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.34,1:48:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会做什么梦\N{\rEng}When we have shuffled off this mortal coil
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.14,1:48:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这必然令人踌躇\N{\rEng}Must give us pause.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.03,1:49:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,正是这份顾虑\N{\rEng}There's the respect
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.25,1:49:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们心甘陷入这漫长的苦难\N{\rEng}That makes calamity of so long life.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.44,1:49:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谁甘心忍受这人世的鞭挞和嘲辱\N{\rEng}Who would bear the whips and scorns of time,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.42,1:49:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,压迫的屈辱\N{\rEng}The oppressor's wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.75,1:49:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,傲慢的蔑辱\N{\rEng}the proud man's contumely,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.25,1:49:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,心碎的羞辱\N{\rEng}The pangs of despised love,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.35,1:49:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,法律的冷辱\N{\rEng}the law's delay,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.67,1:49:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,官吏的欺辱 以及小人对\N{\rEng}The insolence of office, and the spurns
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.59,1:49:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,勤勤恳恳老实人的侮辱\N{\rEng}That patient merit of the unworthy take,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.84,1:49:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,否则当一把匕首就能解脱\N{\rEng}When he himself might his quietus make
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.85,1:49:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谁不愿意？\N{\rEng}With a bare bodkin?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.42,1:49:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谁愿背负这重担\N{\rEng}Who would fardels bear,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.99,1:49:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,撑着这疲惫的身躯呻吟 流汗\N{\rEng}To grunt and sweat under a weary life,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.42,1:49:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是死后那无人归返\N{\rEng}But that the dread of something after death,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.27,1:49:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,未知的国度令我们恐惧\N{\rEng}The undiscovered country from whose bourn
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.55,1:49:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,困扰了我们的意志\N{\rEng}No traveler returns, puzzles the will,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.71,1:49:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,使我们宁愿忍受眼前的不幸...\N{\rEng}And makes us rather bear those ills...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.44,1:49:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位\N{\rEng}En garde!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.64,1:50:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一剑\N{\rEng}One!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.67,1:50:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没有击中\N{\rEng}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.11,1:50:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,中了 很明显的一剑\N{\rEng}A hit, a palpable hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.30,1:50:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子一定会胜利\N{\rEng}Our son shall win!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.70,1:50:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧 再来 - 格特鲁德 别喝\N{\rEng}- Well, again! - Gertrude, do not drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.29,1:50:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又是一剑 你自己说中没中\N{\rEng}Another hit! What say you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.44,1:51:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我一剑\N{\rEng}Have at you now!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.85,1:51:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,王后怎么了？\N{\rEng}How does the queen?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.19,1:51:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定是晕血了\N{\rEng}She swoons to see them bleed.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.93,1:51:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 是那酒 那酒\N{\rEng}No, no, the drink, the drink!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.46,1:51:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我心爱的哈姆雷特\N{\rEng}Oh, my dear Hamlet.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.55,1:51:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我中毒了\N{\rEng}I am poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.32,1:51:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 恶毒的阴谋\N{\rEng}Oh, villainy!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.80,1:51:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 把门锁上\N{\rEng}Ho, let the door be locked!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.68,1:51:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,奸贼 揪出来\N{\rEng}Treachery! Seek it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.73,1:51:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆雷特 奸贼就在这儿\N{\rEng}It is here, Hamlet.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.48,1:51:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哈姆雷特 你也要死了\N{\rEng}Hamlet, thou art slain.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.30,1:52:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没有药能救得了你\N{\rEng}No medicine in the world can do thee good.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.75,1:52:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你活不到半个钟头了\N{\rEng}In thee, there is not half an hour's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.67,1:52:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都是国王做的孽\N{\rEng}The king's to blame!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.09,1:52:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,剑头也有毒药？\N{\rEng}The point envenomed, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.95,1:52:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么好 毒药 也给你\N{\rEng}Then, venom, to thy work!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.86,1:52:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个乱伦的 血腥的丹麦的魔王\N{\rEng}Here, thou incestuous, murderous, damned Dane!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.27,1:52:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,给我喝...\N{\rEng}Drink...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.89,1:52:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喝下这杯毒酒\N{\rEng}Drink off this potion!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.28,1:52:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你那心爱的珍珠在里面吗？\N{\rEng}Is thy union here?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.28,1:52:38.84,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【心爱的珍珠: 具双关 既指原著中的珍珠 又指婚姻】
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.86,1:52:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我的母亲一道去吧\N{\rEng}Follow my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.96,1:53:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我死了\N{\rEng}I am dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.84,1:53:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可你还活着\N{\rEng}Thou livest.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.68,1:53:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,请将我的故事与大义\N{\rEng}Report me and my cause aright
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.77,1:53:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如实告知尚不知情的人吧\N{\rEng}To the unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.86,1:53:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,若你曾对我怀有深情与敬重\N{\rEng}If thou didst ever hold me in thy heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.98,1:53:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,暂且别去享那极乐\N{\rEng}Absent thee from felicity awhile,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.24,1:53:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,留在这残酷的尘世 隐忍着痛苦\N{\rEng}And in this harsh world draw thy breath in pain
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.34,1:53:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去把我的故事讲清\N{\rEng}To tell my story.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.34,1:53:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我要死了\N{\rEng}Ah, I die!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.17,1:54:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这剧毒正夺去我的意志\N{\rEng}The potent poison quite o'ercrows my spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.89,1:55:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,余下的只有沉寂\N{\rEng}The rest is silence.
