Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.52,2:00:46.33,Credit,,0,0,0,,{\an8\move(960,1609,960,-422)\fs35\b1\fnSource Han Serif SC}本故事是对莎士比亚文学遗产的多层致敬。 \N草药意象直接呼应《哈姆雷特》中欧菲莉亚的悲剧台词；\N男孩女孩的换装设定则致敬了《威尼斯商人》《皆大欢喜》和《第十二夜》中的经典桥段；\N而安妮丝列出的多个意象（空间、洞穴、悬崖、隧道、大海、虚空与未知国度）\N亦呼应了莎翁多部作品中常见的主题。\N\N鉴于娱乐性与学术性的平衡考量，本作翻译以剧情呈现为主，\N尊重导演的创意表达，对莎翁文学深层意义的阐释有限，敬请理解。\N\N欢迎加入我们的 Telegram / IRC 社群深入交流讨论 @MontageSubs\N\N字幕许可 CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.39,2:01:07.09,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 我的知更鸟啊 飞向了那绿林 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ My Robin to the greenwood will go ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.18,2:01:10.36,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 那里有橡树也有白蜡 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Where the oak and the ash ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.43,2:01:13.76,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 还有那尖刺的荆棘 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ And the briars do grow ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.82,2:01:17.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 爱人啊 你可好啊 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ How fares my love ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.18,2:01:20.88,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 夜幕吞噬了森林 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ As the darkness falls ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.16,2:01:23.89,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 深陷那幽闭的树影里 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ There within ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.91,2:01:27.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 你可好啊 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Those tangled walls? ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.27,2:01:30.57,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 爱人啊 你可好啊 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ How fares my love ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.58,2:01:34.35,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 夜幕吞噬了森林 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ As the darkness falls ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.46,2:01:37.64,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 深陷那幽闭的树影里 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ There within ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.65,2:01:41.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 你可好啊 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Those tangled walls? ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.26,2:01:50.36,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 绿林啊 近在咫尺 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ The greenwood is near ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.48,2:01:53.77,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 绿林啊 又远在天边 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ And the greenwood is far ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.91,2:01:57.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 无数的危险啊 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ And many a danger ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.79,2:02:00.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 潜伏在那里 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Befalls a man there ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.55,2:02:03.81,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 我祈求那些树啊 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ I pray that those trees ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.93,2:02:07.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 还我男孩来 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Will return my boy ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.32,2:02:10.89,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 只因那只温柔的知更鸟 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ For sweet bonny Robin ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.91,2:02:14.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 是我仅有的幸福 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Is all my joy ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.10,2:02:17.15,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 我祈求那些树啊 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ I pray that those trees ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.34,2:02:20.67,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 还我男孩来 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Will return my boy ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.68,2:02:24.24,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 只因那只温柔的知更鸟 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ For sweet bonny Robin ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.25,2:02:27.82,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 是我仅有的幸福 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Is all my joy. ♪
